{"type":"message","id":"c95fa7f2","parentId":"d0db0f8e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T01:48:42.150Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering documentation creation**\n\nThe user mentioned that they want to create a development document in Feishu, but I need more information about the content. Since we don’t have actual development docs, perhaps a template or skeleton would work. I could also look into drafting something based on the current discussion, but it feels like I should clarify what they want first. I’m thinking a generic \"开发文档（待补充）\" might help, but I worry it could end up being useless without more specific details.\n\n**Exploring document creation**\n\nI’m looking into the skills for creating a document. It might be worth checking for existing content in the workspace, but there probably isn't any. I want to ask the user, “Which development document do you want me to generate? Please share the content or let me know if I should start with a template.” Since the user mentioned storing the document, I should create a standard template titled \"开发文档（草稿）\" in a personal space, just to keep things clear and useful as a draft. However, it seems I can't directly use a tool for creating it.\n\n**Investigating available tools**\n\nIt seems I have the skill for document creation, but the specific tool isn't listed. I think there's a direct function like feishu_create_doc that should be accessible. But wait, it doesn't appear under the developer message functions namespace. However, the skills indicate it likely exists in this environment, possibly accessible via openclaw. I need to clarify how to use this function or find a way to work around its absence. It's a bit confusing, but I'm determined to figure it out!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ql7e88WJVzw9VgLngIIlMBeu","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -R \"feishu_create_doc\\|create doc\\|云文档\" -n /usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin 2>/dev/null | head -50","workdir":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"code889","model":"gpt-5.4-mini","usage":{"input":332,"output":2890,"cacheRead":29184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32406,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774057707837}}
{"type":"message","id":"1df888dc","parentId":"c95fa7f2","timestamp":"2026-03-21T01:48:42.235Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ql7e88WJVzw9VgLngIIlMBeu","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/feishu-fetch-doc/SKILL.md:4:  获取飞书云文档内容。返回文档的 Markdown 内容，支持处理文档中的图片、文件和画板（需配合 feishu_doc_media 工具）。\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/feishu-fetch-doc/SKILL.md:9:获取飞书云文档的 Markdown 内容（Lark-flavored 格式）。\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/feishu-fetch-doc/SKILL.md:58:知识库链接（`/wiki/TOKEN`）背后可能是云文档、电子表格、多维表格等不同类型的文档。当不确定类型时, **不能直接假设是云文档**，必须先查询实际类型。\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/feishu-update-doc/SKILL.md:4:  更新飞书云文档。支持 7 种更新模式：追加、覆盖、定位替换、全文替换、前/后插入、删除。\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/feishu-update-doc/SKILL.md:9:更新飞书云文档内容，支持 7 种更新模式。优先使用局部更新（replace_range/append/insert_before/insert_after），慎用 overwrite（会清空文档重写，可能丢失图片、评论等）。\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/feishu-create-doc/SKILL.md:4:  创建飞书云文档。从 Lark-flavored Markdown 内容创建新的飞书云文档，支持指定创建位置（文件夹/知识库/知识空间）。\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/feishu-create-doc/SKILL.md:9:通过 MCP 调用 `create-doc`，从 Lark-flavored Markdown 内容创建一个新的飞书云文档。\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/tools/mcp/doc/fetch.d.ts:6:  * 查看云文档内容（返回标题与 Markdown，支持分页）\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/tools/mcp/doc/fetch.js:6:  * 查看云文档内容（返回标题与 Markdown，支持分页）\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/tools/mcp/doc/fetch.js:33:        description: \"获取飞书云文档内容，返回文档标题和 Markdown 格式内容。支持分页获取大文档。\",\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/tools/mcp/doc/create.d.ts:6:  * 从 Markdown 创建云文档（支持异步 task_id 查询）\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/tools/mcp/doc/index.js:40:    api.logger.info?.(\"feishu_doc: Registered feishu_fetch_doc, feishu_create_doc, feishu_update_doc\");\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/tools/mcp/doc/update.js:6:  * 更新云文档（overwrite/append/replace_range/replace_all/insert_before/insert_after/delete_range，支持异步 task_id 查询）\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/tools/mcp/doc/update.js:60:        description: \"更新云文档（overwrite/append/replace_range/replace_all/insert_before/insert_after/delete_range，支持异步 task_id 查询）\",\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/tools/mcp/doc/update.d.ts:6:  * 更新云文档（overwrite/append/replace_range/replace_all/insert_before/insert_after/delete_range，支持异步 task_id 查询）\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/tools/mcp/doc/create.js:6:  * 从 Markdown 创建云文档（支持异步 task_id 查询）\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/tools/mcp/doc/create.js:36:        name: \"feishu_create_doc\",\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/tools/mcp/doc/create.js:38:        toolActionKey: \"feishu_create_doc.default\",\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/tools/mcp/doc/create.js:40:        description: \"从 Markdown 创建云文档（支持异步 task_id 查询）\",\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/tools/oapi/drive/doc-comments.js:5:  * feishu_doc_comments tool -- 云文档评论管理\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/tools/oapi/drive/doc-comments.js:7:  * 支持获取、创建、解决/恢复云文档评论\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/tools/oapi/drive/doc-comments.js:36:        description: \"云文档token或wiki节点token(可从文档URL获取)。如果是wiki token，会自动转换为实际文档的obj_token\",\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/tools/oapi/drive/doc-comments.js:161:        description: \"【以用户身份】管理云文档评论。支持: \" +\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/src/tools/oapi/drive/doc-