{"type":"message","id":"277f28ff","parentId":"794e9bba","timestamp":"2026-03-21T02:07:42.170Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_PnJixzk5pAHpNzWlr1WkY4dG","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Initializing skill: memory-mechanism\n   Location: /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills\n   Resources: references\n\n[OK] Created skill directory: /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/memory-mechanism\n[OK] Created SKILL.md\n[OK] Created references/\n\n[OK] Skill 'memory-mechanism' initialized successfully at /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/memory-mechanism\n\nNext steps:\n1. Edit SKILL.md to complete the TODO items and update the description\n2. Add resources to scripts/, references/, and assets/ as needed\n3. Run the validator when ready to check the skill structure"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":111,"aggregated":"Initializing skill: memory-mechanism\n   Location: /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills\n   Resources: references\n\n[OK] Created skill directory: /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/memory-mechanism\n[OK] Created SKILL.md\n[OK] Created references/\n\n[OK] Skill 'memory-mechanism' initialized successfully at /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/memory-mechanism\n\nNext steps:\n1. Edit SKILL.md to complete the TODO items and update the description\n2. Add resources to scripts/, references/, and assets/ as needed\n3. Run the validator when ready to check the skill structure","cwd":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774058862145}}
