{"type":"message","id":"f9e3b740","parentId":"1a63761a","timestamp":"2026-03-21T07:48:12.513Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 15:48:12 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7 [msg:om_x100b54d09d7a10bcb3314ff28452a1d, post]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54d09d7a10bcb3314ff28452a1d\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 15:48 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7\"\n}\n```\n\n好的，请完成\n- **结算页/新手引导交互稿**\n- **规则引擎测试数据集**\n- **AI 基准局面集**\n- **完整研发排期甘特表**"}],"timestamp":1774079292508}}
