{"type":"message","id":"3822199b","parentId":"ea09ce4b","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:25:53.449Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Structuring a miniprogram**\n\nI'm considering creating a simple folder structure under chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram. I'll include files like app.json and several page directories for index, game, result, and tutorial. It seems important to implement a skeleton with placeholders and basic state. I want to ensure there are no package conflicts and maybe create a test dataset as JSON. Given the user's request, I ought to reflect this in my code, including a UI skeleton and a test runner for the JSON data.\n\n**Creating a test dataset**\n\nI need to create a structured test dataset, which can be stored in a file for use in tests. Currently, these tests are hard-coded, but I want to refactor them so they can load from a JSON fixture. Given that there are requests for A and then B, I might add datasets while keeping the existing tests. I plan to create `test/fixtures/rule-cases.json` and `test/fixtures/ai-cases.json`, modifying tests to utilize these or adding a new file that loops over the cases. It's best to standardize the dataset as JSON for easier use.\n\n**Structuring JSON for Board Pieces**\n\nI need to be careful with the board pieces structure in JSON. Instead of using full board objects, I could simplify to a board spec that includes side and piece entries. I’m considering implementing a helper in test/data, and it might require importing JSON in Node using assert. With Node 22, I could use import assertions, but it feels safer to rely on fs readFileSync and JSON.parse. I'll create a loader utility and maybe set up fixtures for tests. I wonder how the user would like the structure handled.\n\n**Creating WeChat Mini Game Structure**\n\nI’m planning to port to a WeChat mini-game, so I’ll need to create a structure with several files: miniprogram/app.json, app.js, app.wxss, and pages for index, game, result, and tutorial. I want to set up a skeleton with basic data and navigation methods, since there won't be actual WeChat code execution. I might need a shared game-state utility as well, but I can’t use ES modules directly in the WeChat environment unless I bundle them. I’ll implement this and write the necessary files.\n\n**Setting Up Test Fixtures**\n\nI’m considering creating `test/fixtures/rule_cases.json` and `test/fixtures/ai_cases.json`, along with `test/fixtures.test.js` to utilize these files. I should think about updating the current tests to incorporate these new cases, but I could also keep the existing tests as they are and add new ones that use the fixtures. This way, I can ensure I’m covering the necessary scenarios without losing the previous test structure.\n\n**Creating test and app files**\n\nI’m thinking about creating a `test/fixtures.test.js` to read these tests and run assertions using engine functions. It seems like there’s some duplication in the current tests, and maybe we should update or remove what's not needed. I wonder if it would be simpler to create a dataset from these existing tests. Still, I could create a new test file with old ones intact. \n\nRegarding the B UI skeleton, I’ll make a `miniprogram/` folder with app files and pages, like `index`, `game`, `result`, and `tutorial`.\n\n**Structuring the app skeleton**\n\nI’m thinking about the basic skeleton for the app. I’ll include data elements like `title`, `mode: 'ai'`, `side: 'red'`, `statusText`, `canUndo: false`, `tips`, and `boardSummary`. There’ll be methods such as `onLoad`, `startLocalGame`, `startAIGame`, and `goToResult`, but I won’t integrate the actual engine just yet. \n\nI envision the index page with navigation cards for game, tutorial, and result. The result page will show the winner and a summary, while the tutorial will list the rules. The `app.js` can also manage global data!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_zxIRr6b8AzMtB4vcQEO5D23b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -e\nBASE=/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame\nmkdir -p \"$BASE/test/fixtures\" \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/index\" \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/game\" \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/result\" \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/tutorial\" \"$BASE/miniprogram/utils\"\ncat > \"$BASE/test/fixtures/rule-cases.json\" <<'EOF'\n[\n  {\n    \"name\": \"initial board\",\n    \"board\": {\n      \"currentSide\": \"red\",\n      \"pieces\": [\n        { \"id\": \"b-r1\", \"type\": \"rook\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 0, \"y\": 0 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-h1\", \"type\": \"horse\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 1, \"y\": 0 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-e1\", \"type\": \"elephant\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 2, \"y\": 0 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-a1\", \"type\": \"advisor\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 3, \"y\": 0 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-g\", \"type\": \"general\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 0 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-a2\", \"type\": \"advisor\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 5, \"y\": 0 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-e2\", \"type\": \"elephant\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 6, \"y\": 0 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-h2\", \"type\": \"horse\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 7, \"y\": 0 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-r2\", \"type\": \"rook\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 8, \"y\": 0 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-c1\", \"type\": \"cannon\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 1, \"y\": 2 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-c2\", \"type\": \"cannon\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 7, \"y\": 2 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-s1\", \"type\": \"soldier\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 0, \"y\": 3 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-s2\", \"type\": \"soldier\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 2, \"y\": 3 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-s3\", \"type\": \"soldier\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 3 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-s4\", \"type\": \"soldier\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 6, \"y\": 3 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-s5\", \"type\": \"soldier\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 8, \"y\": 3 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-r1\", \"type\": \"rook\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 0, \"y\": 9 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-h1\", \"type\": \"horse\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 1, \"y\": 9 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-e1\", \"type\": \"elephant\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 2, \"y\": 9 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-a1\", \"type\": \"advisor\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 3, \"y\": 9 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-g\", \"type\": \"general\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 9 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-a2\", \"type\": \"advisor\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 5, \"y\": 9 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-e2\", \"type\": \"elephant\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 6, \"y\": 9 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-h2\", \"type\": \"horse\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 7, \"y\": 9 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-r2\", \"type\": \"rook\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 8, \"y\": 9 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-c1\", \"type\": \"cannon\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 1, \"y\": 7 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-c2\", \"type\": \"cannon\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 7, \"y\": 7 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-s1\", \"type\": \"soldier\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 0, \"y\": 6 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-s2\", \"type\": \"soldier\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 2, \"y\": 6 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-s3\", \"type\": \"soldier\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 6 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-s4\", \"type\": \"soldier\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 6, \"y\": 6 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-s5\", \"type\": \"soldier\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 8, \"y\": 6 }\n      ],\n      \"expect\": {\n        \"pieceCount\": 32,\n        \"currentSide\": \"red\"\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"rook clear file\",\n    \"board\": {\n      \"currentSide\": \"red\",\n      \"pieces\": [\n        { \"id\": \"r-g\", \"type\": \"general\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 9 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-g\", \"type\": \"general\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 0 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-r\", \"type\": \"rook\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 0, \"y\": 9 }\n      ],\n      \"expect\": {\n        \"rookMoves\": [\n          { \"x\": 0, \"y\": 8 },\n          { \"x\": 0, \"y\": 7 },\n          { \"x\": 0, \"y\": 6 }\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"soldier after river\",\n    \"board\": {\n      \"currentSide\": \"red\",\n      \"pieces\": [\n        { \"id\": \"r-g\", \"type\": \"general\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 3, \"y\": 9 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-g\", \"type\": \"general\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 5, \"y\": 0 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-s\", \"type\": \"soldier\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 4 }\n      ],\n      \"expect\": {\n        \"soldierMoves\": [\n          { \"x\": 4, \"y\": 3 },\n          { \"x\": 3, \"y\": 4 },\n          { \"x\": 5, \"y\": 4 }\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"flying general\",\n    \"board\": {\n      \"currentSide\": \"red\",\n      \"pieces\": [\n        { \"id\": \"r-g\", \"type\": \"general\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 9 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-g\", \"type\": \"general\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 0 }\n      ],\n      \"expect\": {\n        \"redInCheck\": true,\n        \"blackInCheck\": true\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"cannon capture\",\n    \"board\": {\n      \"currentSide\": \"red\",\n      \"pieces\": [\n        { \"id\": \"r-g\", \"type\": \"general\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 9 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-g\", \"type\": \"general\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 0 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-c\", \"type\": \"cannon\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 7 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-s\", \"type\": \"soldier\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 4 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-screen\", \"type\": \"soldier\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 6 }\n      ],\n      \"expect\": {\n        \"cannonCapture\": { \"x\": 4, \"y\": 4 }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n]\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/test/fixtures/ai-cases.json\" <<'EOF'\n[\n  {\n    \"name\": \"tactical move exists\",\n    \"side\": \"red\",\n    \"depth\": 1,\n    \"board\": {\n      \"currentSide\": \"red\",\n      \"pieces\": [\n        { \"id\": \"r-g\", \"type\": \"general\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 9 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-g\", \"type\": \"general\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 0 },\n        { \"id\": \"r-r\", \"type\": \"rook\", \"side\": \"red\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 8 },\n        { \"id\": \"b-s\", \"type\": \"soldier\", \"side\": \"black\", \"x\": 4, \"y\": 5 }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"expect\": {\n      \"hasLegalMove\": true\n    }\n  }\n]\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/test/fixtures.test.js\" <<'EOF'\nimport test from 'node:test';\nimport assert from 'node:assert/strict';\nimport { readFileSync } from 'node:fs';\nimport { createInitialBoard, Side } from '../src/game/board.js';\nimport { getLegalMoves, isInCheck } from '../src/game/rules.js';\nimport { searchBestMove } from '../src/game/ai.js';\n\nconst rulesCases = JSON.parse(readFileSync(new URL('./fixtures/rule-cases.json', import.meta.url), 'utf8'));\nconst aiCases = JSON.parse(readFileSync(new URL('./fixtures/ai-cases.json', import.meta.url), 'utf8'));\n\nfunction toBoard(spec) {\n  return {\n    pieces: spec.pieces.map((piece) => ({\n      id: piece.id,\n      type: piece.type,\n      side: piece.side,\n      pos: { x: piece.x, y: piece.y },\n      alive: true,\n    })),\n    currentSide: spec.currentSide,\n    selectedPieceId: null,\n    lastMove: null,\n    moveHistory: [],\n    status: 'playing',\n    winner: null,\n  };\n}\n\nfor (const testCase of rulesCases) {\n  test(`fixture: ${testCase.name}`, () => {\n    const board = toBoard(testCase.board);\n    const expect = testCase.board.expect;\n\n    if (expect.pieceCount) {\n      assert.equal(board.pieces.length, expect.pieceCount);\n    }\n    if (expect.currentSide) {\n      assert.equal(board.currentSide, expect.currentSide);\n    }\n\n    if (expect.rookMoves) {\n      const rookMoves = getLegalMoves(board, Side.RED).filter((move) => move.pieceId === 'r-r');\n      for (const expectedMove of expect.rookMoves) {\n        assert.ok(rookMoves.some((move) => move.to.x === expectedMove.x && move.to.y === expectedMove.y));\n      }\n    }\n\n    if (expect.soldierMoves) {\n      const soldierMoves = getLegalMoves(board, Side.RED).filter((move) => move.pieceId === 'r-s');\n      for (const expectedMove of expect.soldierMoves) {\n        assert.ok(soldierMoves.some((move) => move.to.x === expectedMove.x && move.to.y === expectedMove.y));\n      }\n    }\n\n    if (expect.redInCheck !== undefined) {\n      assert.equal(isInCheck(board, Side.RED), expect.redInCheck);\n    }\n    if (expect.blackInCheck !== undefined) {\n      assert.equal(isInCheck(board, Side.BLACK), expect.blackInCheck);\n    }\n\n    if (expect.cannonCapture) {\n      const cannonMoves = getLegalMoves(board, Side.RED).filter((move) => move.pieceId === 'r-c');\n      assert.ok(cannonMoves.some((move) => move.to.x === expect.cannonCapture.x && move.to.y === expect.cannonCapture.y));\n    }\n  });\n}\n\nfor (const testCase of aiCases) {\n  test(`AI fixture: ${testCase.name}`, () => {\n    const board = toBoard(testCase.board);\n    const move = searchBestMove(board, { side: testCase.side, depth: testCase.depth, timeLimitMs: 20 });\n    assert.ok(move);\n    if (testCase.expect.hasLegalMove) {\n      const legal = getLegalMoves(board, testCase.side === 'red' ? Side.RED : Side.BLACK);\n      assert.ok(legal.some((candidate) =>\n        candidate.pieceId === move.pieceId &&\n        candidate.to.x === move.to.x &&\n        candidate.to.y === move.to.y\n      ));\n    }\n  });\n}\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/app.js\" <<'EOF'\nApp({\n  globalData: {\n    gameConfig: {\n      title: '中国象棋',\n      defaultMode: 'ai',\n      defaultSide: 'red',\n    },\n  },\n});\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/app.json\" <<'EOF'\n{\n  \"pages\": [\n    \"pages/index/index\",\n    \"pages/game/game\",\n    \"pages/result/result\",\n    \"pages/tutorial/tutorial\"\n  ],\n  \"window\": {\n    \"navigationBarTitleText\": \"中国象棋\",\n    \"navigationBarBackgroundColor\": \"#f6e8c3\",\n    \"navigationBarTextStyle\": \"black\",\n    \"backgroundColor\": \"#f8f4e8\"\n  }\n}\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/app.wxss\" <<'EOF'\npage {\n  background: #f8f4e8;\n  color: #1f1f1f;\n  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;\n}\n.button-primary {\n  background: #b8362d;\n  color: #fff;\n  border-radius: 16rpx;\n}\n.card {\n  background: #fff;\n  border-radius: 20rpx;\n  padding: 24rpx;\n  margin: 20rpx;\n  box-shadow: 0 8rpx 24rpx rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n}\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/utils/game-state.js\" <<'EOF'\nexport function createGameState() {\n  return {\n    mode: 'ai',\n    side: 'red',\n    status: 'ready',\n    winner: null,\n    moveCount: 0,\n    message: '准备开始',\n  };\n}\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/index/index.json\" <<'EOF'\n{\n  \"navigationBarTitleText\": \"中国象棋\"\n}\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/index/index.js\" <<'EOF'\nPage({\n  data: {\n    title: '中国象棋微信小游戏',\n    subtitle: '先跑起来，再变强',\n  },\n\n  goGame() {\n    wx.navigateTo({ url: '/pages/game/game' });\n  },\n\n  goTutorial() {\n    wx.navigateTo({ url: '/pages/tutorial/tutorial' });\n  },\n});\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/index/index.wxml\" <<'EOF'\n<view class=\"card\">\n  <view class=\"title\">{{title}}</view>\n  <view class=\"subtitle\">{{subtitle}}</view>\n  <button class=\"button-primary\" bindtap=\"goGame\">开始对局</button>\n  <button bindtap=\"goTutorial\">查看规则引导</button>\n</view>\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/index/index.wxss\" <<'EOF'\n.title { font-size: 40rpx; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16rpx; }\n.subtitle { color: #666; margin-bottom: 28rpx; }\nbutton { margin-top: 16rpx; }\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/game/game.json\" <<'EOF'\n{\n  \"navigationBarTitleText\": \"对局\"\n}\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/game/game.js\" <<'EOF'\nimport { createGameState } from '../../utils/game-state';\n\nPage({\n  data: {\n    state: createGameState(),\n    boardLabel: '棋盘区域占位',\n    tips: [\n      '这里后续接入规则引擎',\n      '这里后续接入落子、悔棋、提示',\n      '这里后续接入人机 / 本地双人 / 在线匹配'\n    ],\n  },\n\n  onLoad() {\n    this.setData({\n      state: {\n        ...this.data.state,\n        message: '游戏页已就绪',\n      },\n    });\n  },\n\n  startGame() {\n    this.setData({\n      state: {\n        ...this.data.state,\n        status: 'playing',\n        message: '对局开始',\n      },\n    });\n  },\n\n  goResult() {\n    wx.navigateTo({ url: '/pages/result/result' });\n  },\n});\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/game/game.wxml\" <<'EOF'\n<view class=\"card\">\n  <view class=\"section-title\">{{state.message}}</view>\n  <view class=\"board-placeholder\">{{boardLabel}}</view>\n  <view class=\"meta\">模式：{{state.mode}} · 执子：{{state.side}}</view>\n  <button class=\"button-primary\" bindtap=\"startGame\">开始对局</button>\n  <button bindtap=\"goResult\">去结算页</button>\n</view>\n<view class=\"card\">\n  <view class=\"section-title\">后续接入点</view>\n  <view wx:for=\"{{tips}}\" wx:key=\"*this\">- {{item}}</view>\n</view>\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/game/game.wxss\" <<'EOF'\n.section-title { font-size: 32rpx; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 16rpx; }\n.board-placeholder {\n  height: 520rpx;\n  border: 2rpx dashed #c9b08a;\n  border-radius: 20rpx;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  color: #8a6d3b;\n  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff8ea, #f5ead3);\n  margin-bottom: 20rpx;\n}\n.meta { color: #666; margin-bottom: 20rpx; }\nbutton { margin-top: 16rpx; }\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/result/result.json\" <<'EOF'\n{\n  \"navigationBarTitleText\": \"结算\"\n}\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/result/result.js\" <<'EOF'\nPage({\n  data: {\n    winnerText: '结果占位',\n    summary: '这里后续展示胜负、用时和复盘入口。',\n  },\n\n  goHome() {\n    wx.reLaunch({ url: '/pages/index/index' });\n  },\n});\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/result/result.wxml\" <<'EOF'\n<view class=\"card\">\n  <view class=\"section-title\">{{winnerText}}</view>\n  <view>{{summary}}</view>\n  <button class=\"button-primary\" bindtap=\"goHome\">返回首页</button>\n</view>\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/result/result.wxss\" <<'EOF'\n.section-title { font-size: 34rpx; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16rpx; }\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/tutorial/tutorial.json\" <<'EOF'\n{\n  \"navigationBarTitleText\": \"新手引导\"\n}\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/tutorial/tutorial.js\" <<'EOF'\nPage({\n  data: {\n    steps: [\n      '目标：将对方将死',\n      '规则：每个棋子按固定走法移动',\n      '辅助：支持提示、悔棋、复盘'\n    ],\n  },\n});\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/tutorial/tutorial.wxml\" <<'EOF'\n<view class=\"card\">\n  <view class=\"section-title\">新手引导</view>\n  <view wx:for=\"{{steps}}\" wx:key=\"*this\">{{index + 1}}. {{item}}</view>\n</view>\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/pages/tutorial/tutorial.wxss\" <<'EOF'\n.section-title { font-size: 34rpx; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16rpx; }\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/project.config.json\" <<'EOF'\n{\n  \"miniprogramRoot\": \"./\",\n  \"projectname\": \"chinese-chess-minigame\",\n  \"compileType\": \"miniprogram\",\n  \"libVersion\": \"3.5.0\"\n}\nEOF\ncat > \"$BASE/miniprogram/sitemap.json\" <<'EOF'\n{\n  \"rules\": [\n    { \"action\": \"allow\", \"page\": \"pages/index/index\" },\n    { \"action\": \"allow\", \"page\": \"pages/game/game\" },\n    { \"action\": \"allow\", \"page\": \"pages/result/result\" },\n    { \"action\": \"allow\", \"page\": \"pages/tutorial/tutorial\" }\n  ]\n}\nEOF\nnpm test --prefix \"$BASE\"","workdir":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace","timeout":120}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"code889","model":"gpt-5.4-mini","usage":{"input":768,"output":8557,"cacheRead":59392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68717,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774088709136}}
