{"type":"message","id":"a7b52ce9","parentId":"754a9166","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:27:00.061Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"已先做 **A**，再做了 **B**。现在都落地了，而且测试全绿。\n\n### A. 测试数据集\n我新增了标准化 fixture：\n\n- `test/fixtures/rule-cases.json`\n- `test/fixtures/ai-cases.json`\n- `test/fixtures.test.js`\n\n覆盖了这些场景：\n- 初始局面\n- 车的直线行走\n- 过河兵的横向移动\n- 飞将\n- 炮打隔子吃子\n- AI 合法落子\n\n### B. 微信小游戏 UI 骨架\n我也搭了最小可运行的小游戏结构：\n\n- `miniprogram/app.js`\n- `miniprogram/app.json`\n- `miniprogram/app.wxss`\n- `miniprogram/pages/index/*`\n- `miniprogram/pages/game/*`\n- `miniprogram/pages/result/*`\n- `miniprogram/pages/tutorial/*`\n- `miniprogram/utils/game-state.js`\n- `miniprogram/project.config.json`\n- `miniprogram/sitemap.json`\n\n目前 UI 是**占位骨架**，但页面流已经通了：\n- 首页\n- 对局页\n- 结算页\n- 新手引导页\n\n### 结果\n我又跑了一次测试：\n\n- **12/12 通过**\n\n### 现在最适合的下一步\n我建议继续做这个：\n\n**C. 把 UI 和规则引擎真正接起来**\n具体就是：\n- 棋盘渲染\n- 点击选子 / 落子\n- 高亮合法走法\n- 走子后切换回合\n- AI 回合自动走子\n- 悔棋 / 复盘入口\n\n如果你要，我下一条可以直接开始把 **棋盘交互 + 落子逻辑** 接上。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"code889","model":"gpt-5.4-mini","usage":{"input":838,"output":404,"cacheRead":74752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75994,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774088815159}}
