{"type":"message","id":"dd6bec19","parentId":"0286ea62","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:42:45.764Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering game match summary**\n\nI’m looking into saving a match summary at the game's end. If there's a checkmate or draw, I need to detect that after each move and navigate to a results page. I could modify the `commitMove` function to save the result when the game status isn't \"playing.\" I want to maintain a move list and board history for easier navigation. We might need to export helper functions from the chess engine and consider using wx storage keys for results.\n\n**Planning for game replay**\n\nI need to set up a replay feature, possibly by creating an `initialBoard` using `createInitialBoard()` or storing it in the summary with moves. Since the initial board is deterministic, I can just reconstruct it. For replaying, if there’s no existing helper, I can utilize `replayMoves` from `src/game/replay.js`, though I'm unsure about the module system since it doesn't fit the miniprogram side. It might be better to add `replayMoves` as an export from the chess engine, allowing the results page to reconstruct progress by applying the first N moves.\n\n**Considering match store implementation**\n\nI’m thinking about adding `finalizeMatch(board)` and maybe saving a snapshot. Creating `miniprogram/utils/match-store.js` sounds like a neat idea. I should inspect if existing tests cover the miniprogram, but I'm guessing they probably don't. Should I add a node test for the match store? It might not be necessary, but no regression would be a good goal. Maybe I should check the package files, but that might not be needed. I might end up using exec and cat > files.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ePM4Vun0IGNkMCnHUxfNPf27","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"const MATCH_STORAGE_KEY = 'chess:lastMatch';\n\nfunction saveLastMatch(match) {\n  wx.setStorageSync(MATCH_STORAGE_KEY, match);\n}\n\nfunction loadLastMatch() {\n  try {\n    return wx.getStorageSync(MATCH_STORAGE_KEY) || null;\n  } catch (error) {\n    return null;\n  }\n}\n\nfunction clearLastMatch() {\n  try {\n    wx.removeStorageSync(MATCH_STORAGE_KEY);\n  } catch (error) {\n    // noop\n  }\n}\n\nmodule.exports = {\n  saveLastMatch,\n  loadLastMatch,\n  clearLastMatch,\n};\n","file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/utils/match-store.js","path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/utils/match-store.js"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_YtTL8SYhntpUN8JrLyLNmrmb","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"const { createGameState } = require('../../utils/game-state');\nconst {\n  Side,\n  createInitialBoard,\n  cloneBoard,\n  getPieceAt,\n  getLegalMoves,\n  advanceGame,\n  searchBestMove,\n  pieceLabel,\n} = require('../../utils/chess-engine');\nconst { saveLastMatch } = require('../../utils/match-store');\n\nfunction coordKey(x, y) {\n  return `${x}:${y}`;\n}\n\nfunction buildBoardView(board, selectedPieceId, legalMoves) {\n  const legalMap = new Set((legalMoves || []).map((move) => coordKey(move.to.x, move.to.y)));\n  const lastMoveMap = board.lastMove\n    ? new Set([coordKey(board.lastMove.from.x, board.lastMove.from.y), coordKey(board.lastMove.to.x, board.lastMove.to.y)])\n    : new Set();\n\n  const rows = [];\n  for (let y = 0; y < 10; y += 1) {\n    const cells = [];\n    for (let x = 0; x < 9; x += 1) {\n      const piece = getPieceAt(board, x, y);\n      const selected = piece && piece.id === selectedPieceId;\n      const legalTarget = legalMap.has(coordKey(x, y));\n      const lastMove = lastMoveMap.has(coordKey(x, y));\n      cells.push({\n        x,\n        y,\n        key: coordKey(x, y),\n        piece,\n        text: piece ? pieceLabel(piece) : '',\n        selected,\n        legalTarget,\n        lastMove,\n      });\n    }\n    rows.push({ y, cells });\n  }\n  return rows;\n}\n\nPage({\n  data: {\n    state: createGameState(),\n    board: createInitialBoard(),\n    boardRows: [],\n    selectedPieceId: null,\n    legalMoves: [],\n    tips: [\n      '点棋子选中，再点可落位置',\n      '红方先手，目前默认人机对战',\n      '后续可继续接入悔棋、提示、复盘'\n    ],\n  },\n\n  onLoad() {\n    this.boardHistory = [];\n    this.aiTimer = null;\n    this.refreshBoard('游戏页已就绪');\n  },\n\n  onUnload() {\n    if (this.aiTimer) clearTimeout(this.aiTimer);\n  },\n\n  refreshBoard(message, overrideLegalMoves) {\n    const legalMoves = getLegalMoves(this.data.board, this.data.board.currentSide);\n    const boardRows = buildBoardView(this.data.board, this.data.selectedPieceId, overrideLegalMoves || this.data.legalMoves);\n    const summary = this.getStatusText(this.data.board, message);\n    this.setData({\n      state: {\n        ...this.data.state,\n        status: this.data.board.status,\n        winner: this.data.board.winner,\n        side: this.data.board.currentSide,\n        moveCount: this.data.board.moveHistory.length,\n        message: summary,\n      },\n      boardRows,\n      legalMoves,\n      boardLabel: summary,\n    });\n  },\n\n  getStatusText(board, fallback) {\n    if (board.status === 'checkmate') {\n      return board.winner === Side.RED ? '红方胜，已将死' : '黑方胜，已将死';\n    }\n    if (board.status === 'draw') return '平局';\n    if (board.status === 'check') return `${board.currentSide === Side.RED ? '红方' : '黑方'}被将军`;\n    return fallback || `${board.currentSide === Side.RED ? '红方' : '黑方'}走子`;\n  },\n\n  saveMatchResult(finalBoard) {\n    const winnerText = finalBoard.status === 'draw'\n      ? '平局'\n      : finalBoard.winner === Side.RED\n        ? '红方胜'\n        : '黑方胜';\n    const replayMoves = finalBoard.moveHistory.map((move) => ({\n      pieceId: move.pieceId,\n      from: move.from,\n      to: move.to,\n      capturedPieceId: move.capturedPieceId,\n    }));\n\n    saveLastMatch({\n      finishedAt: Date.now(),\n      status: finalBoard.status,\n      winner: finalBoard.winner,\n      winnerText,\n      moveCount: finalBoard.moveHistory.length,\n      summary: this.getStatusText(finalBoard),\n      moves: replayMoves,\n      finalBoard: cloneBoard(finalBoard),\n    });\n  },\n\n  resetGame() {\n    if (this.aiTimer) clearTimeout(this.aiTimer);\n    this.boardHistory = [];\n    this.setData({\n      board: createInitialBoard(),\n      selectedPieceId: null,\n      legalMoves: [],\n    });\n    this.refreshBoard('对局已重开');\n  },\n\n  undoMove() {\n    if (!this.boardHistory || !this.boardHistory.length) return;\n    if (this.aiTimer) clearTimeout(this.aiTimer);\n    const previous = this.boardHistory.pop();\n    this.setData({\n      board: cloneBoard(previous),\n      selectedPieceId: null,\n      legalMoves: [],\n    });\n    this.refreshBoard('已悔棋一步');\n  },\n\n  onCellTap(e) {\n    if (this.data.board.status === 'checkmate' || this.data.board.status === 'draw') return;\n    if (this.data.board.currentSide === Side.BLACK) return;\n\n    const x = Number(e.currentTarget.dataset.x);\n    const y = Number(e.currentTarget.dataset.y);\n    const piece = getPieceAt(this.data.board, x, y);\n    const selectedPieceId = this.data.selectedPieceId;\n    const selectedMoves = this.data.legalMoves;\n    const legalMove = selectedMoves.find((move) => move.to.x === x && move.to.y === y);\n\n    if (legalMove) {\n      this.commitMove(legalMove, '你走了一步');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    if (piece && piece.side === Side.RED && this.data.board.currentSide === Side.RED) {\n      const moves = getLegalMoves(this.data.board, Side.RED).filter((move) => move.pieceId === piece.id);\n      this.setData({\n        selectedPieceId: piece.id,\n        legalMoves: moves,\n      });\n      this.refreshBoard(`${pieceLabel(piece)}已选中`, moves);\n      return;\n    }\n\n    if (selectedPieceId) {\n      this.setData({ selectedPieceId: null, legalMoves: [] });\n      this.refreshBoard('取消选中');\n    }\n  },\n\n  finishIfNeeded(nextBoard) {\n    if (nextBoard.status === 'playing') return false;\n    this.saveMatchResult(nextBoard);\n    const resultUrl = `/pages/result/result?status=${nextBoard.status}&winner=${nextBoard.winner || ''}`;\n    wx.reLaunch({ url: resultUrl });\n    return true;\n  },\n\n  commitMove(move, message) {\n    this.boardHistory.push(cloneBoard(this.data.board));\n    const nextBoard = advanceGame(this.data.board, move);\n    this.setData({\n      board: nextBoard,\n      selectedPieceId: null,\n      legalMoves: [],\n    });\n    this.refreshBoard(message);\n\n    if (this.finishIfNeeded(nextBoard)) return;\n\n    if (nextBoard.status === 'playing' && nextBoard.currentSide === Side.BLACK) {\n      this.scheduleAiMove();\n    }\n  },\n\n  scheduleAiMove() {\n    if (this.aiTimer) clearTimeout(this.aiTimer);\n    this.aiTimer = setTimeout(() => {\n      this.aiTimer = null;\n      const move = searchBestMove(this.data.board, { side: Side.BLACK, depth: 1, timeLimitMs: 80 });\n      if (!move) {\n        this.refreshBoard('AI 无合法走法');\n        return;\n      }\n      this.commitMove(move, 'AI 已落子');\n    }, 180);\n  },\n\n  startGame() {\n    this.resetGame();\n  },\n\n  goResult() {\n    wx.navigateTo({ url: '/pages/result/result' });\n  },\n});\n","file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/game/game.js","path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/game/game.js"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_QoBiW1oHR2ow7rYSZbjyldfJ","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"const { createInitialBoard, replayMoves, pieceLabel, getPieceAt } = require('../../utils/chess-engine');\nconst { loadLastMatch, clearLastMatch } = require('../../utils/match-store');\n\nfunction formatWinnerText(match) {\n  if (!match) return '暂无对局结果';\n  if (match.status === 'draw') return '本局平局';\n  return `${match.winnerText || '对局结束'}，恭喜 ${match.winner === 'red' ? '红方' : '黑方'}`;\n}\n\nfunction buildReplayRows(board) {\n  const rows = [];\n  for (let y = 0; y < 10; y += 1) {\n    const cells = [];\n    for (let x = 0; x < 9; x += 1) {\n      const piece = getPieceAt(board, x, y);\n      cells.push({\n        x,\n        y,\n        key: `${x}:${y}`,\n        piece,\n        text: piece ? pieceLabel(piece) : '',\n      });\n    }\n    rows.push({ y, cells });\n  }\n  return rows;\n}\n\nPage({\n  data: {\n    winnerText: '结果占位',\n    summary: '这里后续展示胜负、用时和复盘入口。',\n    match: null,\n    replayIndex: -1,\n    replayBoardRows: [],\n    replayTitle: '复盘尚未加载',\n    movePreview: [],\n  },\n\n  onLoad(query = {}) {\n    this.loadMatch(query);\n  },\n\n  onShow() {\n    if (!this.data.match) {\n      this.loadMatch({});\n    }\n  },\n\n  loadMatch(query) {\n    const match = loadLastMatch();\n    if (!match) {\n      this.setData({\n        match: null,\n        winnerText: '暂无结果',\n        summary: '还没有可展示的对局。先回到首页开始一局吧。',\n        replayIndex: -1,\n        replayBoardRows: buildReplayRows(createInitialBoard()),\n        replayTitle: '空白棋盘',\n        movePreview: [],\n      });\n      return;\n    }\n\n    const targetStatus = query.status || match.status;\n    const winnerText = formatWinnerText({ ...match, status: targetStatus });\n    const movePreview = match.moves.map((move, index) => ({\n      index,\n      label: `${index + 1}. ${move.pieceId} → (${move.to.x},${move.to.y})${move.capturedPieceId ? ` 吃 ${move.capturedPieceId}` : ''}`,\n    }));\n\n    this.setData({\n      match,\n      winnerText,\n      summary: `共 ${match.moveCount} 步 · ${match.summary || ''}`,\n      replayIndex: match.moves.length - 1,\n      movePreview,\n    });\n    this.renderReplay(match.moves.length - 1);\n  },\n\n  renderReplay(index) {\n    const match = this.data.match;\n    if (!match) return;\n    const safeIndex = Math.max(-1, Math.min(index, match.moves.length - 1));\n    const board = safeIndex >= 0 ? replayMoves(createInitialBoard(), match.moves.slice(0, safeIndex + 1)) : createInitialBoard();\n    this.setData({\n      replayIndex: safeIndex,\n      replayBoardRows: buildReplayRows(board),\n      replayTitle: safeIndex < 0 ? '开局局面' : `第 ${safeIndex + 1} 步后局面`,\n    });\n  },\n\n  prevStep() {\n    if (!this.data.match || this.data.replayIndex < 0) return;\n    this.renderReplay(this.data.replayIndex - 1);\n  },\n\n  nextStep() {\n    if (!this.data.match) return;\n    this.renderReplay(this.data.replayIndex + 1);\n  },\n\n  jumpToStart() {\n    this.renderReplay(-1);\n  },\n\n  jumpToEnd() {\n    if (!this.data.match) return;\n    this.renderReplay(this.data.match.moves.length - 1);\n  },\n\n  playAgain() {\n    clearLastMatch();\n    wx.reLaunch({ url: '/pages/game/game' });\n  },\n\n  goHome() {\n    wx.reLaunch({ url: '/pages/index/index' });\n  },\n});\n","file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/result/result.js","path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/result/result.js"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_jc9wObEojQWb6r83Ls9CEhaj","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"<view class=\"card\">\n  <view class=\"section-title\">{{winnerText}}</view>\n  <view class=\"summary\">{{summary}}</view>\n  <view class=\"meta\">复盘：{{replayTitle}}</view>\n\n  <view class=\"actions\">\n    <button class=\"button-primary\" bindtap=\"playAgain\">再来一局</button>\n    <button bindtap=\"goHome\">返回首页</button>\n  </view>\n</view>\n\n<view class=\"card\">\n  <view class=\"section-title\">复盘棋盘</view>\n  <view class=\"board-shell\">\n    <view class=\"board-grid\">\n      <block wx:for=\"{{replayBoardRows}}\" wx:key=\"y\">\n        <view class=\"board-row\">\n          <block wx:for=\"{{item.cells}}\" wx:key=\"key\">\n            <view class=\"board-cell\">\n              <view wx:if=\"{{cell.piece}}\" class=\"piece piece-{{cell.piece.side}}\">{{cell.text}}</view>\n            </view>\n          </block>\n        </view>\n      </block>\n    </view>\n  </view>\n\n  <view class=\"actions\">\n    <button bindtap=\"jumpToStart\">回到开局</button>\n    <button bindtap=\"prevStep\">上一步</button>\n    <button bindtap=\"nextStep\">下一步</button>\n    <button bindtap=\"jumpToEnd\">到结尾</button>\n  </view>\n</view>\n\n<view class=\"card\">\n  <view class=\"section-title\">走子列表</view>\n  <view wx:if=\"{{movePreview.length}}\">\n    <view wx:for=\"{{movePreview}}\" wx:key=\"index\">{{item.label}}</view>\n  </view>\n  <view wx:else>暂无走子记录</view>\n</view>\n","file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/result/result.wxml","path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/result/result.wxml"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_AQs2ESlb3r1gqqvKqs2tXdyr","name":"write","arguments":{"content":".section-title { font-size: 34rpx; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16rpx; }\n.summary { margin-bottom: 8rpx; }\n.meta { color: #666; margin-bottom: 16rpx; }\n.actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16rpx; margin-bottom: 16rpx; }\n.board-shell {\n  padding: 18rpx;\n  background: #ead9b4;\n  border-radius: 24rpx;\n  margin-bottom: 20rpx;\n}\n.board-grid {\n  background: #f8e8c4;\n  border: 2rpx solid #a07b46;\n  border-radius: 16rpx;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n.board-row { display: flex; }\n.board-cell {\n  width: 52rpx;\n  height: 52rpx;\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n  border-right: 1rpx solid rgba(160, 123, 70, 0.25);\n  border-bottom: 1rpx solid rgba(160, 123, 70, 0.25);\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n}\n.board-row:last-child .board-cell { border-bottom: none; }\n.board-cell:last-child { border-right: none; }\n.piece {\n  width: 34rpx;\n  height: 34rpx;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  font-size: 20rpx;\n  font-weight: 700;\n}\n.piece-red {\n  background: #f8efe2;\n  color: #b8362d;\n  border: 2rpx solid #c06b63;\n}\n.piece-black {\n  background: #f6f1e8;\n  color: #333;\n  border: 2rpx solid #666;\n}\n","file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/result/result.wxss","path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/result/result.wxss"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"code889","model":"gpt-5.4-mini","usage":{"input":2263,"output":6522,"cacheRead":57344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66129,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774089729601}}
