{"type":"message","id":"648bafa4","parentId":"cc3b3b2b","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:56:19.655Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_UiN6zPdC8xeNoMjrfmBG9wvA","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/game/game.js","limit":260,"offset":1,"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/game/game.js"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_yc3WNqpJuE5o7Wa9Ls6tdrex","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/result/result.js","limit":260,"offset":1,"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/result/result.js"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_UoJkLnJnFpnkeXW7X1fDAL3N","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/utils/match-store.js","limit":200,"offset":1,"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/utils/match-store.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"code889","model":"gpt-5.4-mini","usage":{"input":1003,"output":862,"cacheRead":78848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80713,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774090573546}}
{"type":"message","id":"4eba8cbc","parentId":"648bafa4","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:56:19.666Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_UiN6zPdC8xeNoMjrfmBG9wvA","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"const { createGameState } = require('../../utils/game-state');\nconst {\n  Side,\n  createInitialBoard,\n  cloneBoard,\n  getPieceAt,\n  getLegalMoves,\n  advanceGame,\n  searchBestMove,\n  pieceLabel,\n} = require('../../utils/chess-engine');\nconst { saveLastMatch } = require('../../utils/match-store');\n\nfunction coordKey(x, y) {\n  return `${x}:${y}`;\n}\n\nfunction buildBoardView(board, selectedPieceId, legalMoves) {\n  const legalMap = new Set((legalMoves || []).map((move) => coordKey(move.to.x, move.to.y)));\n  const lastMoveMap = board.lastMove\n    ? new Set([coordKey(board.lastMove.from.x, board.lastMove.from.y), coordKey(board.lastMove.to.x, board.lastMove.to.y)])\n    : new Set();\n\n  const rows = [];\n  for (let y = 0; y < 10; y += 1) {\n    const cells = [];\n    for (let x = 0; x < 9; x += 1) {\n      const piece = getPieceAt(board, x, y);\n      const selected = piece && piece.id === selectedPieceId;\n      const legalTarget = legalMap.has(coordKey(x, y));\n      const lastMove = lastMoveMap.has(coordKey(x, y));\n      cells.push({\n        x,\n        y,\n        key: coordKey(x, y),\n        piece,\n        text: piece ? pieceLabel(piece) : '',\n        selected,\n        legalTarget,\n        lastMove,\n      });\n    }\n    rows.push({ y, cells });\n  }\n  return rows;\n}\n\nPage({\n  data: {\n    state: createGameState(),\n    board: createInitialBoard(),\n    boardRows: [],\n    selectedPieceId: null,\n    legalMoves: [],\n    tips: [\n      '点棋子选中，再点可落位置',\n      '红方先手，目前默认人机对战',\n      '后续可继续接入悔棋、提示、复盘'\n    ],\n  },\n\n  onLoad() {\n    this.boardHistory = [];\n    this.aiTimer = null;\n    this.refreshBoard('游戏页已就绪');\n  },\n\n  onUnload() {\n    if (this.aiTimer) clearTimeout(this.aiTimer);\n  },\n\n  refreshBoard(message, overrideLegalMoves) {\n    const legalMoves = getLegalMoves(this.data.board, this.data.board.currentSide);\n    const boardRows = buildBoardView(this.data.board, this.data.selectedPieceId, overrideLegalMoves || this.data.legalMoves);\n    const summary = this.getStatusText(this.data.board, message);\n    this.setData({\n      state: {\n        ...this.data.state,\n        status: this.data.board.status,\n        winner: this.data.board.winner,\n        side: this.data.board.currentSide,\n        moveCount: this.data.board.moveHistory.length,\n        message: summary,\n      },\n      boardRows,\n      legalMoves,\n      boardLabel: summary,\n    });\n  },\n\n  getStatusText(board, fallback) {\n    if (board.status === 'checkmate') {\n      return board.winner === Side.RED ? '红方胜，已将死' : '黑方胜，已将死';\n    }\n    if (board.status === 'draw') return '平局';\n    if (board.status === 'check') return `${board.currentSide === Side.RED ? '红方' : '黑方'}被将军`;\n    return fallback || `${board.currentSide === Side.RED ? '红方' : '黑方'}走子`;\n  },\n\n  saveMatchResult(finalBoard) {\n    const winnerText = finalBoard.status === 'draw'\n      ? '平局'\n      : finalBoard.winner === Side.RED\n        ? '红方胜'\n        : '黑方胜';\n    const replayMoves = finalBoard.moveHistory.map((move) => ({\n      pieceId: move.pieceId,\n      from: move.from,\n      to: move.to,\n      capturedPieceId: move.capturedPieceId,\n    }));\n\n    saveLastMatch({\n      finishedAt: Date.now(),\n      status: finalBoard.status,\n      winner: finalBoard.winner,\n      winnerText,\n      moveCount: finalBoard.moveHistory.length,\n      summary: this.getStatusText(finalBoard),\n      moves: replayMoves,\n      finalBoard: cloneBoard(finalBoard),\n    });\n  },\n\n  resetGame() {\n    if (this.aiTimer) clearTimeout(this.aiTimer);\n    this.boardHistory = [];\n    this.setData({\n      board: createInitialBoard(),\n      selectedPieceId: null,\n      legalMoves: [],\n    });\n    this.refreshBoard('对局已重开');\n  },\n\n  undoMove() {\n    if (!this.boardHistory || !this.boardHistory.length) return;\n    if (this.aiTimer) clearTimeout(this.aiTimer);\n    const previous = this.boardHistory.pop();\n    this.setData({\n      board: cloneBoard(previous),\n      selectedPieceId: null,\n      legalMoves: [],\n    });\n    this.refreshBoard('已悔棋一步');\n  },\n\n  onCellTap(e) {\n    if (this.data.board.status === 'checkmate' || this.data.board.status === 'draw') return;\n    if (this.data.board.currentSide === Side.BLACK) return;\n\n    const x = Number(e.currentTarget.dataset.x);\n    const y = Number(e.currentTarget.dataset.y);\n    const piece = getPieceAt(this.data.board, x, y);\n    const selectedPieceId = this.data.selectedPieceId;\n    const selectedMoves = this.data.legalMoves;\n    const legalMove = selectedMoves.find((move) => move.to.x === x && move.to.y === y);\n\n    if (legalMove) {\n      this.commitMove(legalMove, '你走了一步');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    if (piece && piece.side === Side.RED && this.data.board.currentSide === Side.RED) {\n      const moves = getLegalMoves(this.data.board, Side.RED).filter((move) => move.pieceId === piece.id);\n      this.setData({\n        selectedPieceId: piece.id,\n        legalMoves: moves,\n      });\n      this.refreshBoard(`${pieceLabel(piece)}已选中`, moves);\n      return;\n    }\n\n    if (selectedPieceId) {\n      this.setData({ selectedPieceId: null, legalMoves: [] });\n      this.refreshBoard('取消选中');\n    }\n  },\n\n  finishIfNeeded(nextBoard) {\n    if (nextBoard.status === 'playing') return false;\n    this.saveMatchResult(nextBoard);\n    const resultUrl = `/pages/result/result?status=${nextBoard.status}&winner=${nextBoard.winner || ''}`;\n    wx.reLaunch({ url: resultUrl });\n    return true;\n  },\n\n  commitMove(move, message) {\n    this.boardHistory.push(cloneBoard(this.data.board));\n    const nextBoard = advanceGame(this.data.board, move);\n    this.setData({\n      board: nextBoard,\n      selectedPieceId: null,\n      legalMoves: [],\n    });\n    this.refreshBoard(message);\n\n    if (this.finishIfNeeded(nextBoard)) return;\n\n    if (nextBoard.status === 'playing' && nextBoard.currentSide === Side.BLACK) {\n      this.scheduleAiMove();\n    }\n  },\n\n  scheduleAiMove() {\n    if (this.aiTimer) clearTimeout(this.aiTimer);\n    this.aiTimer = setTimeout(() => {\n      this.aiTimer = null;\n      const move = searchBestMove(this.data.board, { side: Side.BLACK, depth: 1, timeLimitMs: 80 });\n      if (!move) {\n        this.refreshBoard('AI 无合法走法');\n        return;\n      }\n      this.commitMove(move, 'AI 已落子');\n    }, 180);\n  },\n\n  startGame() {\n    this.resetGame();\n  },\n\n  goResult() {\n    wx.navigateTo({ url: '/pages/result/result' });\n  },\n});\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774090579658}}
{"type":"message","id":"d531aefe","parentId":"4eba8cbc","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:56:19.680Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_yc3WNqpJuE5o7Wa9Ls6tdrex","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"const { createInitialBoard, replayMoves, pieceLabel, getPieceAt } = require('../../utils/chess-engine');\nconst { loadLastMatch, clearLastMatch } = require('../../utils/match-store');\n\nfunction formatWinnerText(match) {\n  if (!match) return '暂无对局结果';\n  if (match.status === 'draw') return '本局平局';\n  return `${match.winnerText || '对局结束'}，恭喜 ${match.winner === 'red' ? '红方' : '黑方'}`;\n}\n\nfunction buildReplayRows(board) {\n  const rows = [];\n  for (let y = 0; y < 10; y += 1) {\n    const cells = [];\n    for (let x = 0; x < 9; x += 1) {\n      const piece = getPieceAt(board, x, y);\n      cells.push({\n        x,\n        y,\n        key: `${x}:${y}`,\n        piece,\n        text: piece ? pieceLabel(piece) : '',\n      });\n    }\n    rows.push({ y, cells });\n  }\n  return rows;\n}\n\nPage({\n  data: {\n    winnerText: '结果占位',\n    summary: '这里后续展示胜负、用时和复盘入口。',\n    match: null,\n    replayIndex: -1,\n    replayBoardRows: [],\n    replayTitle: '复盘尚未加载',\n    movePreview: [],\n  },\n\n  onLoad(query = {}) {\n    this.loadMatch(query);\n  },\n\n  onShow() {\n    if (!this.data.match) {\n      this.loadMatch({});\n    }\n  },\n\n  loadMatch(query) {\n    const match = loadLastMatch();\n    if (!match) {\n      this.setData({\n        match: null,\n        winnerText: '暂无结果',\n        summary: '还没有可展示的对局。先回到首页开始一局吧。',\n        replayIndex: -1,\n        replayBoardRows: buildReplayRows(createInitialBoard()),\n        replayTitle: '空白棋盘',\n        movePreview: [],\n      });\n      return;\n    }\n\n    const targetStatus = query.status || match.status;\n    const winnerText = formatWinnerText({ ...match, status: targetStatus });\n    const movePreview = match.moves.map((move, index) => ({\n      index,\n      label: `${index + 1}. ${move.pieceId} → (${move.to.x},${move.to.y})${move.capturedPieceId ? ` 吃 ${move.capturedPieceId}` : ''}`,\n    }));\n\n    this.setData({\n      match,\n      winnerText,\n      summary: `共 ${match.moveCount} 步 · ${match.summary || ''}`,\n      replayIndex: match.moves.length - 1,\n      movePreview,\n    });\n    this.renderReplay(match.moves.length - 1);\n  },\n\n  renderReplay(index) {\n    const match = this.data.match;\n    if (!match) return;\n    const safeIndex = Math.max(-1, Math.min(index, match.moves.length - 1));\n    const board = safeIndex >= 0 ? replayMoves(createInitialBoard(), match.moves.slice(0, safeIndex + 1)) : createInitialBoard();\n    this.setData({\n      replayIndex: safeIndex,\n      replayBoardRows: buildReplayRows(board),\n      replayTitle: safeIndex < 0 ? '开局局面' : `第 ${safeIndex + 1} 步后局面`,\n    });\n  },\n\n  prevStep() {\n    if (!this.data.match || this.data.replayIndex < 0) return;\n    this.renderReplay(this.data.replayIndex - 1);\n  },\n\n  nextStep() {\n    if (!this.data.match) return;\n    this.renderReplay(this.data.replayIndex + 1);\n  },\n\n  jumpToStart() {\n    this.renderReplay(-1);\n  },\n\n  jumpToEnd() {\n    if (!this.data.match) return;\n    this.renderReplay(this.data.match.moves.length - 1);\n  },\n\n  playAgain() {\n    clearLastMatch();\n    wx.reLaunch({ url: '/pages/game/game' });\n  },\n\n  goHome() {\n    wx.reLaunch({ url: '/pages/index/index' });\n  },\n});\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774090579672}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf5f18d5","parentId":"d531aefe","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:56:19.689Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_UoJkLnJnFpnkeXW7X1fDAL3N","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"const MATCH_STORAGE_KEY = 'chess:lastMatch';\n\nfunction saveLastMatch(match) {\n  wx.setStorageSync(MATCH_STORAGE_KEY, match);\n}\n\nfunction loadLastMatch() {\n  try {\n    return wx.getStorageSync(MATCH_STORAGE_KEY) || null;\n  } catch (error) {\n    return null;\n  }\n}\n\nfunction clearLastMatch() {\n  try {\n    wx.removeStorageSync(MATCH_STORAGE_KEY);\n  } catch (error) {\n    // noop\n  }\n}\n\nmodule.exports = {\n  saveLastMatch,\n  loadLastMatch,\n  clearLastMatch,\n};\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774090579683}}
{"type":"message","id":"26f3f6e5","parentId":"bf5f18d5","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:56:33.152Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating project needs**\n\nI need to inspect the project package and test infrastructure. I’m thinking of checking the package files to see if any tests already exist that aren’t affecting the miniprogram. Maybe I could add a small JavaScript helper for match formatting, but that might not be necessary. It would be good if I make the result and game pages more robust, and perhaps add navigation to the result page and implement fallback behavior. Let’s see what can be improved!\n\n**Ensuring memory management**\n\nI need to set up an auto-jump to the result page with stored data when a game ends. I’m considering whether I should append to memory using a command that avoids file overwrites. It seems important to ensure we store durable memories after work. I'll need to avoid duplicates, possibly by summarizing further progress. I should also check the tail before appending new lines. Lastly, I might fix the result page's formatWinnerText for draws to ensure it's accurate.\n\n**Considering code enhancements**\n\nI'm thinking about adding a move history or temporary state to the match store to preserve the final board. We already have finalBoard stored, and it could be helpful to include replay moves. Right now, `replayMoves` in replay.js just returns the board after moves, but it has some dependencies that might complicate things. Maybe I should check the current repo to see if we have tests for the result page or the app. If not, I could create a utility for replay view and introduce tests. That could make the code more complete and testable!\n\n**Planning utility functions**\n\nI'm considering creating a file called `miniprogram/utils/match-replay.js`, which would include functions like `formatWinnerText`, `buildMovePreview`, and `buildReplayRows`. However, these functions are already used in the result page, so maybe it's not necessary. I could add a button to the result page for resuming to a specific step, but since it's already step-by-step, it might not be required. Also, does the app.json title need updating? I don't think so. It feels more like I should focus on appending concise new bullets for clarity.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_BDoie2vRb49KFUFC2ES6eV8R","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat >> /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/2026-03-21.md <<'EOF'\n- 结算页/复盘链路已进一步固化：最近一次对局会被写入本地存储，结算页可按走子序列逐步回放，且对局结束后会自动跳转到结果页。\n- 结果页现在兼具“胜负展示 + 复盘导航”两个职责，支持回到开局、前后步进和重新开局。\nEOF","workdir":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"code889","model":"gpt-5.4-mini","usage":{"input":3424,"output":2224,"cacheRead":79360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85008,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774090579688}}
