{"type":"message","id":"fbbf78f9","parentId":"f60aec2a","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:58:10.482Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 18:58:01 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7 [msg:om_x100b54d3d5471ca4b49b432b418b9fb]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54d3d5471ca4b49b432b418b9fb\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 18:58 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7\"\n}\n```\n\n评估一下，下一步做什么最好"}],"timestamp":1774090690476}}
{"type":"message","id":"687c763b","parentId":"fbbf78f9","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:58:17.397Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating next steps**\n\nI need to find the best way to answer the user's question about the next step. It looks like inspecting my memory is essential since it involves prior work, decisions, dates, preferences, and todos. I'll start with a memory search as per the instructions. I should also consider reading my current memory about the project context. Using memory_search seems mandatory, especially regarding the current project state. I may need to check the workspace if necessary, but focusing on the memory search is the priority.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bK2KmYVzr7oy0eEPmSZBs5JG","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"maxResults":5,"minScore":0.2,"query":"中国象棋 微信小游戏 当前下一步 最适合 做什么 结算页 复盘 提示 悔棋 在线匹配"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"code889","model":"gpt-5.4-mini","usage":{"input":786,"output":271,"cacheRead":82944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84001,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774090690478}}
