{"type":"message","id":"6f7ab74a","parentId":"651e3b69","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:58:26.214Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Assessing UX and protocol needs**\n\nI want to ensure the user has reliable UX first, then maybe focus on an online matching protocol. If they want the highest leverage, I could suggest making the settlement page a formal end-of-game state and standardizing the result data structure. It seems like that part is mostly done already. I should probably include a prioritized list in my recommendations. I can offer a main recommendation and an alternative if their goals are different.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我建议下一步做 **“对局内体验收口”**，也就是先补：\n\n1. **提示**\n   - 给出当前可走子、将军提醒、推荐一步\n2. **悔棋细节**\n   - 限制悔棋规则\n   - 人机模式下是否允许撤回 AI 的一步\n3. **状态机统一**\n   - `ready / playing / check / checkmate / draw / replay` 这些状态收口成一套稳定流程\n\n### 为什么这一步最值\n因为你现在已经有了：\n- 规则引擎\n- 棋盘交互\n- AI 自动走子\n- 结算页\n- 复盘\n\n这说明 **核心闭环已经通了**。  \n接下来最缺的是 **“玩起来顺不顺”**，而不是再堆新功能。\n\n### 我的判断\n如果按收益排序：\n\n- **第一优先**：提示 + 悔棋 + 状态统一\n- **第二优先**：在线匹配协议抽象\n- **第三优先**：UI 细节打磨和动画\n\n### 结论\n**最好先做提示和悔棋增强。**  \n这一步最能直接提升可玩性，也最能暴露规则/状态机里的边角问题。  \n等这层稳了，再切在线匹配，风险会小很多。\n\n如果你要，我下一条就直接开始做这一步。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"code889","model":"gpt-5.4-mini","usage":{"input":372,"output":932,"cacheRead":83456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84760,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774090697412}}
