{"type":"message","id":"8efe6917","parentId":"2a3c2afc","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:03:20.824Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_miUaXrCqBgWuMEb0hHViAhim","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Page({\n  data: {\n    title: '中国象棋微信小游戏',\n    subtitle: '先跑起来，再变强',\n  },\n\n  goGame() {\n    wx.navigateTo({ url: '/pages/game/game' });\n  },\n\n  goTutorial() {\n    wx.navigateTo({ url: '/pages/tutorial/tutorial' });\n  },\n});\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774091000815}}
{"type":"message","id":"88b87f0f","parentId":"8efe6917","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:03:20.840Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_HQOIzlUcx2ZkNMIEiLZBLHgZ","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"const { createInitialBoard, replayMoves, pieceLabel, getPieceAt } = require('../../utils/chess-engine');\nconst { loadLastMatch, clearLastMatch } = require('../../utils/match-store');\n\nfunction formatWinnerText(match) {\n  if (!match) return '暂无对局结果';\n  if (match.status === 'draw') return '本局平局';\n  return `${match.winnerText || '对局结束'}，恭喜 ${match.winner === 'red' ? '红方' : '黑方'}`;\n}\n\nfunction buildReplayRows(board) {\n  const rows = [];\n  for (let y = 0; y < 10; y += 1) {\n    const cells = [];\n    for (let x = 0; x < 9; x += 1) {\n      const piece = getPieceAt(board, x, y);\n      cells.push({\n        x,\n        y,\n        key: `${x}:${y}`,\n        piece,\n        text: piece ? pieceLabel(piece) : '',\n      });\n    }\n    rows.push({ y, cells });\n  }\n  return rows;\n}\n\nPage({\n  data: {\n    winnerText: '结果占位',\n    summary: '这里后续展示胜负、用时和复盘入口。',\n    match: null,\n    replayIndex: -1,\n    replayBoardRows: [],\n    replayTitle: '复盘尚未加载',\n    movePreview: [],\n  },\n\n  onLoad(query = {}) {\n    this.loadMatch(query);\n  },\n\n  onShow() {\n    if (!this.data.match) {\n      this.loadMatch({});\n    }\n  },\n\n  loadMatch(query) {\n    const match = loadLastMatch();\n    if (!match) {\n      this.setData({\n        match: null,\n        winnerText: '暂无结果',\n        summary: '还没有可展示的对局。先回到首页开始一局吧。',\n        replayIndex: -1,\n        replayBoardRows: buildReplayRows(createInitialBoard()),\n        replayTitle: '空白棋盘',\n        movePreview: [],\n      });\n      return;\n    }\n\n    const targetStatus = query.status || match.status;\n    const winnerText = formatWinnerText({ ...match, status: targetStatus });\n    const movePreview = match.moves.map((move, index) => ({\n      index,\n      label: `${index + 1}. ${move.pieceId} → (${move.to.x},${move.to.y})${move.capturedPieceId ? ` 吃 ${move.capturedPieceId}` : ''}`,\n    }));\n\n    this.setData({\n      match,\n      winnerText,\n      summary: `共 ${match.moveCount} 步 · ${match.summary || ''}`,\n      replayIndex: match.moves.length - 1,\n      movePreview,\n    });\n    this.renderReplay(match.moves.length - 1);\n  },\n\n  renderReplay(index) {\n    const match = this.data.match;\n    if (!match) return;\n    const safeIndex = Math.max(-1, Math.min(index, match.moves.length - 1));\n    const board = safeIndex >= 0 ? replayMoves(createInitialBoard(), match.moves.slice(0, safeIndex + 1)) : createInitialBoard();\n    this.setData({\n      replayIndex: safeIndex,\n      replayBoardRows: buildReplayRows(board),\n      replayTitle: safeIndex < 0 ? '开局局面' : `第 ${safeIndex + 1} 步后局面`,\n    });\n  },\n\n  prevStep() {\n    if (!this.data.match || this.data.replayIndex < 0) return;\n    this.renderReplay(this.data.replayIndex - 1);\n  },\n\n  nextStep() {\n    if (!this.data.match) return;\n    this.renderReplay(this.data.replayIndex + 1);\n  },\n\n  jumpToStart() {\n    this.renderReplay(-1);\n  },\n\n  jumpToEnd() {\n    if (!this.data.match) return;\n    this.renderReplay(this.data.match.moves.length - 1);\n  },\n\n  playAgain() {\n    clearLastMatch();\n    wx.reLaunch({ url: '/pages/game/game' });\n  },\n\n  goHome() {\n    wx.reLaunch({ url: '/pages/index/index' });\n  },\n});\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774091000830}}
{"type":"message","id":"76c3d412","parentId":"88b87f0f","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:03:20.849Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8IFJotZ603XaaxulIujmW5Sy","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Page({\n  data: {\n    steps: [\n      '目标：将对方将死',\n      '规则：每个棋子按固定走法移动',\n      '辅助：支持提示、悔棋、复盘'\n    ],\n  },\n});\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774091000843}}
{"type":"message","id":"2eae2c98","parentId":"76c3d412","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:03:29.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Continuing tool integration**\n\nI need to keep working with the tools and possibly modify the miniprogram to connect to the protocol abstraction. The user specifically mentioned to continue connecting the miniprogram. I should check the current utils for existing chess-engine wrappers or local storage options. It might be necessary to create a protocol helper in the miniprogram using shared source files, but since it can't import node sources, I should consider alternatives for adding online mode and UI controls. Let's delve into more files to explore this further!\n\n**Integrating online features**\n\nI think I need to focus on integrating the online match protocol layer into the miniprogram structure, which involves possibly adding a toggle for online mode and a placeholder. Since there's no backend, I can create a protocol abstraction along with a UI switch to show the room state. I’ll need to read through the current chess-engine utils and inspect result/tutorial pages to understand the interface better. Additionally, I should implement both offline and online mode selection and a protocol state object. Let’s check the current WXMLs to see if I can add buttons!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0aWEYSOgMgBSShnY6PWY7Uh8","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/index/index.wxml","limit":200,"offset":1,"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/index/index.wxml"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_pPTVJ1LrMx3ZVmdHbWMmw6zq","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/result/result.wxml","limit":260,"offset":1,"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/result/result.wxml"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_FTYW4436dr6Of5XGMgRPlhan","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/tutorial/tutorial.wxml","limit":220,"offset":1,"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/tutorial/tutorial.wxml"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_eWhZ1Wtyvvh78jnmR6mSFNE4","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/game/game.js","limit":360,"offset":1,"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/game/game.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"code889","model":"gpt-5.4-mini","usage":{"input":1876,"output":970,"cacheRead":56320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59166,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774091000849}}
{"type":"message","id":"2d88425b","parentId":"2eae2c98","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:03:29.747Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0aWEYSOgMgBSShnY6PWY7Uh8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<view class=\"card\">\n  <view class=\"title\">{{title}}</view>\n  <view class=\"subtitle\">{{subtitle}}</view>\n  <button class=\"button-primary\" bindtap=\"goGame\">开始对局</button>\n  <button bindtap=\"goTutorial\">查看规则引导</button>\n</view>\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774091009737}}
{"type":"message","id":"a0a3c801","parentId":"2d88425b","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:03:29.762Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_pPTVJ1LrMx3ZVmdHbWMmw6zq","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<view class=\"card\">\n  <view class=\"section-title\">{{winnerText}}</view>\n  <view class=\"summary\">{{summary}}</view>\n  <view class=\"meta\">复盘：{{replayTitle}}</view>\n\n  <view class=\"actions\">\n    <button class=\"button-primary\" bindtap=\"playAgain\">再来一局</button>\n    <button bindtap=\"goHome\">返回首页</button>\n  </view>\n</view>\n\n<view class=\"card\">\n  <view class=\"section-title\">复盘棋盘</view>\n  <view class=\"board-shell\">\n    <view class=\"board-grid\">\n      <block wx:for=\"{{replayBoardRows}}\" wx:for-item=\"row\" wx:key=\"y\">\n        <view class=\"board-row\">\n          <block wx:for=\"{{row.cells}}\" wx:for-item=\"cell\" wx:key=\"key\">\n            <view class=\"board-cell\">\n              <view wx:if=\"{{cell.piece}}\" class=\"piece piece-{{cell.piece.side}}\">{{cell.text}}</view>\n            </view>\n          </block>\n        </view>\n      </block>\n    </view>\n  </view>\n\n  <view class=\"actions\">\n    <button bindtap=\"jumpToStart\">回到开局</button>\n    <button bindtap=\"prevStep\">上一步</button>\n    <button bindtap=\"nextStep\">下一步</button>\n    <button bindtap=\"jumpToEnd\">到结尾</button>\n  </view>\n</view>\n\n<view class=\"card\">\n  <view class=\"section-title\">走子列表</view>\n  <view wx:if=\"{{movePreview.length}}\">\n    <view wx:for=\"{{movePreview}}\" wx:key=\"index\">{{item.label}}</view>\n  </view>\n  <view wx:else>暂无走子记录</view>\n</view>\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774091009752}}
{"type":"message","id":"b683575c","parentId":"a0a3c801","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:03:29.773Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_FTYW4436dr6Of5XGMgRPlhan","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<view class=\"card\">\n  <view class=\"section-title\">新手引导</view>\n  <view wx:for=\"{{steps}}\" wx:key=\"*this\">{{index + 1}}. {{item}}</view>\n</view>\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774091009765}}
{"type":"message","id":"2d333520","parentId":"b683575c","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:03:29.783Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_eWhZ1Wtyvvh78jnmR6mSFNE4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"const { createGameState } = require('../../utils/game-state');\nconst {\n  Side,\n  createInitialBoard,\n  cloneBoard,\n  getPieceAt,\n  getLegalMoves,\n  advanceGame,\n  searchBestMove,\n  pieceLabel,\n} = require('../../utils/chess-engine');\nconst { saveLastMatch } = require('../../utils/match-store');\n\nfunction coordKey(x, y) {\n  return `${x}:${y}`;\n}\n\nfunction formatCoord({ x, y }) {\n  return `(${x},${y})`;\n}\n\nfunction buildBoardView(board, selectedPieceId, legalMoves, hintMove) {\n  const legalMap = new Set((legalMoves || []).map((move) => coordKey(move.to.x, move.to.y)));\n  const hintMap = hintMove\n    ? new Set([coordKey(hintMove.from.x, hintMove.from.y), coordKey(hintMove.to.x, hintMove.to.y)])\n    : new Set();\n  const lastMoveMap = board.lastMove\n    ? new Set([coordKey(board.lastMove.from.x, board.lastMove.from.y), coordKey(board.lastMove.to.x, board.lastMove.to.y)])\n    : new Set();\n\n  const rows = [];\n  for (let y = 0; y < 10; y += 1) {\n    const cells = [];\n    for (let x = 0; x < 9; x += 1) {\n      const piece = getPieceAt(board, x, y);\n      const selected = piece && piece.id === selectedPieceId;\n      const legalTarget = legalMap.has(coordKey(x, y));\n      const hintTarget = hintMap.has(coordKey(x, y));\n      const lastMove = lastMoveMap.has(coordKey(x, y));\n      cells.push({\n        x,\n        y,\n        key: coordKey(x, y),\n        piece,\n        text: piece ? pieceLabel(piece) : '',\n        selected,\n        legalTarget,\n        hintTarget,\n        lastMove,\n      });\n    }\n    rows.push({ y, cells });\n  }\n  return rows;\n}\n\nfunction moveToText(move) {\n  if (!move) return '';\n  return `${move.pieceId} ${formatCoord(move.from)} → ${formatCoord(move.to)}`;\n}\n\nPage({\n  data: {\n    state: createGameState(),\n    board: createInitialBoard(),\n    boardRows: [],\n    selectedPieceId: null,\n    legalMoves: [],\n    hintMove: null,\n    hintText: '点击“提示”获取推荐走法',\n    tips: [\n      '点棋子选中，再点可落位置',\n      '红方先手，目前默认人机对战',\n      '提示会推荐当前回合的一步走法'\n    ],\n  },\n\n  onLoad() {\n    this.boardHistory = [];\n    this.aiTimer = null;\n    this.refreshBoard('游戏页已就绪');\n  },\n\n  onUnload() {\n    if (this.aiTimer) clearTimeout(this.aiTimer);\n  },\n\n  refreshBoard(message, overrideLegalMoves, overrideHintMove) {\n    const legalMoves = getLegalMoves(this.data.board, this.data.board.currentSide);\n    const boardRows = buildBoardView(\n      this.data.board,\n      this.data.selectedPieceId,\n      overrideLegalMoves || this.data.legalMoves,\n      overrideHintMove === undefined ? this.data.hintMove : overrideHintMove,\n    );\n    const summary = this.getStatusText(this.data.board, message);\n    this.setData({\n      state: {\n        ...this.data.state,\n        status: this.data.board.status,\n        winner: this.data.board.winner,\n        side: this.data.board.currentSide,\n        moveCount: this.data.board.moveHistory.length,\n        message: summary,\n      },\n      boardRows,\n      legalMoves,\n      boardLabel: summary,\n    });\n  },\n\n  getStatusText(board, fallback) {\n    if (board.status === 'checkmate') {\n      return board.winner === Side.RED ? '红方胜，已将死' : '黑方胜，已将死';\n    }\n    if (board.status === 'draw') return '平局';\n    if (board.status === 'check') return `${board.currentSide === Side.RED ? '红方' : '黑方'}被将军`;\n    return fallback || `${board.currentSide === Side.RED ? '红方' : '黑方'}走子`;\n  },\n\n  saveMatchResult(finalBoard) {\n    const winnerText = finalBoard.status === 'draw'\n      ? '平局'\n      : finalBoard.winner === Side.RED\n        ? '红方胜'\n        : '黑方胜';\n    const replayMoves = finalBoard.moveHistory.map((move) => ({\n      pieceId: move.pieceId,\n      from: move.from,\n      to: move.to,\n      capturedPieceId: move.capturedPieceId,\n    }));\n\n    saveLastMatch({\n      finishedAt: Date.now(),\n      status: finalBoard.status,\n      winner: finalBoard.winner,\n      winnerText,\n      moveCount: finalBoard.moveHistory.length,\n      summary: this.getStatusText(finalBoard),\n      moves: replayMoves,\n      finalBoard: cloneBoard(finalBoard),\n    });\n  },\n\n  resetGame() {\n    if (this.aiTimer) clearTimeout(this.aiTimer);\n    this.boardHistory = [];\n    this.setData({\n      board: createInitialBoard(),\n      selectedPieceId: null,\n      legalMoves: [],\n      hintMove: null,\n      hintText: '点击“提示”获取推荐走法',\n    });\n    this.refreshBoard('对局已重开');\n  },\n\n  undoMove() {\n    if (!this.boardHistory || !this.boardHistory.length) return;\n    if (this.aiTimer) clearTimeout(this.aiTimer);\n\n    const stepsToUndo = this.data.state.mode === 'ai' && this.data.board.currentSide === Side.RED ? 2 : 1;\n    let previous = null;\n    for (let i = 0; i < stepsToUndo; i += 1) {\n      if (!this.boardHistory.length) break;\n      previous = this.boardHistory.pop();\n    }\n    if (!previous) return;\n\n    this.setData({\n      board: cloneBoard(previous),\n      selectedPieceId: null,\n      legalMoves: [],\n      hintMove: null,\n      hintText: stepsToUndo === 2 ? '已悔棋两步，轮到你重新落子' : '已悔棋一步',\n    });\n    this.refreshBoard(stepsToUndo === 2 ? '已悔棋两步' : '已悔棋一步');\n  },\n\n  showHint() {\n    if (this.data.board.status === 'checkmate' || this.data.board.status === 'draw') {\n      this.setData({ hintMove: null, hintText: '对局已结束，无法提示' });\n      this.refreshBoard('对局已结束');\n      return;\n    }\n    if (this.data.board.currentSide !== Side.RED) {\n      this.setData({ hintMove: null, hintText: '当前轮到黑方，先等 AI 走完' });\n      this.refreshBoard('当前轮到黑方');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    const hintMove = searchBestMove(this.data.board, { side: Side.RED, depth: 2, timeLimitMs: 60 });\n    if (!hintMove) {\n      this.setData({ hintMove: null, hintText: '当前没有可用提示' });\n      this.refreshBoard('当前没有可用提示');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    const piece = getPieceAt(this.data.board, hintMove.from.x, hintMove.from.y);\n    const hintText = `${piece ? pieceLabel(piece) : '棋子'} 建议走 ${formatCoord(hintMove.from)} → ${formatCoord(hintMove.to)}`;\n    this.setData({\n      hintMove,\n      hintText,\n      selectedPieceId: piece ? piece.id : null,\n      legalMoves: getLegalMoves(this.data.board, Side.RED).filter((move) => move.pieceId === hintMove.pieceId),\n    });\n    this.refreshBoard('已给出提示', this.data.legalMoves, hintMove);\n  },\n\n  onCellTap(e) {\n    if (this.data.board.status === 'checkmate' || this.data.board.status === 'draw') return;\n    if (this.data.board.currentSide === Side.BLACK) return;\n\n    const x = Number(e.currentTarget.dataset.x);\n    const y = Number(e.currentTarget.dataset.y);\n    const piece = getPieceAt(this.data.board, x, y);\n    const selectedPieceId = this.data.selectedPieceId;\n    const selectedMoves = this.data.legalMoves;\n    const legalMove = selectedMoves.find((move) => move.to.x === x && move.to.y === y);\n\n    if (legalMove) {\n      this.commitMove(legalMove, '你走了一步');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    if (piece && piece.side === Side.RED && this.data.board.currentSide === Side.RED) {\n      const moves = getLegalMoves(this.data.board, Side.RED).filter((move) => move.pieceId === piece.id);\n      this.setData({\n        selectedPieceId: piece.id,\n        legalMoves: moves,\n        hintMove: null,\n        hintText: `已选中 ${pieceLabel(piece)}，可落点已高亮`,\n      });\n      this.refreshBoard(`${pieceLabel(piece)}已选中`, moves, null);\n      return;\n    }\n\n    if (selectedPieceId) {\n      this.setData({ selectedPieceId: null, legalMoves: [], hintMove: null, hintText: '已取消选中' });\n      this.refreshBoard('取消选中', [], null);\n    }\n  },\n\n  finishIfNeeded(nextBoard) {\n    if (nextBoard.status === 'playing') return false;\n    this.saveMatchResult(nextBoard);\n    const resultUrl = `/pages/result/result?status=${nextBoard.status}&winner=${nextBoard.winner || ''}`;\n    wx.reLaunch({ url: resultUrl });\n    return true;\n  },\n\n  commitMove(move, message) {\n    this.boardHistory.push(cloneBoard(this.data.board));\n    const nextBoard = advanceGame(this.data.board, move);\n    this.setData({\n      board: nextBoard,\n      selectedPieceId: null,\n      legalMoves: [],\n      hintMove: null,\n      hintText: message,\n    });\n    this.refreshBoard(message, [], null);\n\n    if (this.finishIfNeeded(nextBoard)) return;\n\n    if (nextBoard.status === 'playing' && nextBoard.currentSide === Side.BLACK) {\n      this.scheduleAiMove();\n    }\n  },\n\n  scheduleAiMove() {\n    if (this.aiTimer) clearTimeout(this.aiTimer);\n    this.aiTimer = setTimeout(() => {\n      this.aiTimer = null;\n      const move = searchBestMove(this.data.board, { side: Side.BLACK, depth: 1, timeLimitMs: 80 });\n      if (!move) {\n        this.setData({ hintMove: null, hintText: 'AI 无合法走法' });\n        this.refreshBoard('AI 无合法走法');\n        return;\n      }\n      this.commitMove(move, 'AI 已落子');\n    }, 180);\n  },\n\n  startGame() {\n    this.resetGame();\n  },\n\n  goResult() {\n    wx.navigateTo({ url: '/pages/result/result' });\n  },\n});\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774091009776}}
{"type":"message","id":"d7129471","parentId":"2d333520","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:04:00.747Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Integrating online protocol**\n\nI need to continue with the small project by integrating an online protocol into the miniprogram. I'll likely have to modify game.js or the result page and potentially utilize the match protocol in the utils. Since the miniprogram uses CommonJS require and our current setup is ESM, I’ll have to create a proxy for the match protocol in CommonJS. It's essential to keep the tests, and I'll need to inspect styles and possibly create additional pages or fields. Let's see how to implement the online protocol layer effectively.\n\n**Creating match protocol**\n\nI’m thinking of creating a miniprogram/utils/match-protocol.js using CommonJS to function as a basic state machine. I’ll connect this to the game page, allowing a toggle between local and online modes with buttons labeled \"本地模式\" and \"在线协议\". If online, the board might not use auto-AI. Since there’s no backend, I can simulate locally to generate envelopes and include a protocol panel. I want to check for previous protocol utility files, but if there aren’t any, I’ll proceed with my plan.\n\n**Integrating protocol into demo page**\n\nI’m considering creating a new demo page to showcase the protocol abstract, but the user wants me to continue integrating it into the miniprogram. I’ll check the current state mode in the game page and add a few elements. \n\nI can include utils/match-protocol.js with enums and functions like createMatchRoom, createEnvelope, applyMatchEvent, and describeMatchRoom, along with local simulation logs. Then, I’ll import this into game.js, adding data.matchRoom and protocolLog, and set up the match room during onLoad.\n\n**Evaluating game UI features**\n\nI’m thinking about adding a \"协议状态\" card to the game UI, featuring a room summary and buttons for different actions like \"切到在线协议\" or \"切回本地AI.\" A cleaner option could be implementing a `mode` switch and using protocol events to manage gameplay, especially for AI moves. \n\nIf in online mode, no auto moves from AI would happen; instead, we'd offer a \"模拟对手\" button for handling remote moves. Additionally, I want an event log for tracking actions. I’ll also consider updating the result page with the mode, but prior memory must be preserved for later.\n\n**Updating game state and protocol**\n\nI need to look at the game page, which currently uses createGameState with 'ai' mode and a red side. I should inspect the game state and consider adding online fields like mode, protocolSummary, and protocolState. Maybe I’ll create these in a new file, `miniprogram/utils/match-protocol.js`, using CommonJS. \n\nI don’t think tests are necessary, so I’ll write the utility functions, including constants for protocol settings and match events, and implement the necessary integration steps on loading and room creation, including handling modes and updates to the game state.\n\n**Resetting the game board**\n\nI need to ensure the board resets properly. When starting a game, the room should reset depending on the mode. If we're in online mode, the commitMove function must handle things differently—after the red move, it shouldn't schedule an AI move. This should clarify how the game behaves in different modes and ensure a seamless experience for users, whether they are playing against an AI or another person online.\n\n**Planning protocol methods**\n\nI'm thinking about what methods to include, like `state`, `protocolRoom`, `protocolLog`, and `hintMove`. I'll consider things like `syncProtocol(room, note)` to synchronize the protocol, and `initProtocolRoom(mode, side maybe)` for setting up. It’s crucial to have a `setMode(mode)` function for adjusting modes and a `startGame` function that resets everything based on the chosen mode. I might also want to look into initializing the room on load.\n\n**Considering undo functionality**\n\nI’m thinking about managing the undo feature in online mode. Perhaps I should just allow undoing the last move, keeping it simple with a one-step approach. I wonder if it's better to keep the current logic but limit it to one step in online mode to avoid confusion with remote actions. The user mentioned wanting an online protocol, so I’ll include that. I'll also plan to update the wxml to add a protocol card below the game board and think about how to style it. Let's start by implementing the utility functions first.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_vMbY0NvbZeSFishh3SS58Shx","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"const { Side, oppositeSide } = require('./chess-engine');\n\nconst PROTOCOL_VERSION = '1.0';\n\nconst MatchMode = Object.freeze({\n  LOCAL: 'local',\n  ONLINE: 'online',\n});\n\nconst MatchState = Object.freeze({\n  IDLE: 'idle',\n  MATCHING: 'matching',\n  READY: 'ready',\n  PLAYING: 'playing',\n  WAITING: 'waiting',\n  SYNCHRONIZING: 'synchronizing',\n  FINISHED: 'finished',\n  ERROR: 'error',\n});\n\nconst MatchEventType = Object.freeze({\n  REQUEST: 'match.request',\n  ACCEPT: 'match.accept',\n  REJECT: 'match.reject',\n  MOVE: 'match.move',\n  ACK: 'match.ack',\n  SYNC: 'match.sync',\n  HEARTBEAT: 'match.heartbeat',\n  RESIGN: 'match.resign',\n  DRAW_OFFER: 'match.draw.offer',\n  DRAW_RESPONSE: 'match.draw.response',\n  ERROR: 'match.error',\n});\n\nfunction createMatchRoom({\n  roomId = null,\n  selfId = null,\n  selfSide = Side.RED,\n  mode = MatchMode.ONLINE,\n  state = MatchState.IDLE,\n  turn = Side.RED,\n  sequence = 0,\n  seed = null,\n} = {}) {\n  return {\n    roomId,\n    selfId,\n    selfSide,\n    mode,\n    state,\n    turn,\n    sequence,\n    seed,\n    opponentId: null,\n    opponentSide: selfSide === Side.RED ? Side.BLACK : Side.RED,\n    lastAckSeq: 0,\n    lastHeartbeatAt: null,\n    lastEventAt: null,\n    lastError: null,\n    result: null,\n    pendingDraw: false,\n    snapshot: null,\n    moveLog: [],\n  };\n}\n\nfunction createEnvelope(type, payload = {}, meta = {}) {\n  return {\n    v: PROTOCOL_VERSION,\n    type,\n    roomId: meta.roomId || null,\n    senderId: meta.senderId || null,\n    seq: meta.seq || 0,\n    ts: meta.ts || Date.now(),\n    payload,\n  };\n}\n\nfunction createMatchRequest({ roomId = null, senderId, desiredSide = null, seed = null } = {}) {\n  return createEnvelope(MatchEventType.REQUEST, { desiredSide, seed }, { roomId, senderId });\n}\n\nfunction createMatchAccept({ roomId, senderId, opponentId, selfSide, seed = null } = {}) {\n  return createEnvelope(MatchEventType.ACCEPT, { opponentId, selfSide, seed }, { roomId, senderId });\n}\n\nfunction createMoveEvent({ roomId, senderId, move, seq = 0 } = {}) {\n  return createEnvelope(MatchEventType.MOVE, { move }, { roomId, senderId, seq });\n}\n\nfunction createAckEvent({ roomId, senderId, ackSeq = 0, hash = null } = {}) {\n  return createEnvelope(MatchEventType.ACK, { ackSeq, hash }, { roomId, senderId });\n}\n\nfunction createSyncEvent({ roomId, senderId, board, turn, moveSeq = 0 } = {}) {\n  return createEnvelope(MatchEventType.SYNC, { board, turn, moveSeq }, { roomId, senderId });\n}\n\nfunction createHeartbeatEvent({ roomId, senderId, ping = Date.now() } = {}) {\n  return createEnvelope(MatchEventType.HEARTBEAT, { ping }, { roomId, senderId });\n}\n\nfunction createResignEvent({ roomId, senderId } = {}) {\n  return createEnvelope(MatchEventType.RESIGN, {}, { roomId, senderId });\n}\n\nfunction createDrawOfferEvent({ roomId, senderId } = {}) {\n  return createEnvelope(MatchEventType.DRAW_OFFER, {}, { roomId, senderId });\n}\n\nfunction createDrawResponseEvent({ roomId, senderId, accepted = false } = {}) {\n  return createEnvelope(MatchEventType.DRAW_RESPONSE, { accepted }, { roomId, senderId });\n}\n\nfunction createErrorEvent({ roomId, senderId, code = 'UNKNOWN', message = 'unknown error' } = {}) {\n  return createEnvelope(MatchEventType.ERROR, { code, message }, { roomId, senderId });\n}\n\nfunction isProtocolEnvelope(value) {\n  return Boolean(\n    value &&\n    typeof value === 'object' &&\n    value.v === PROTOCOL_VERSION &&\n    typeof value.type === 'string' &&\n    value.payload &&\n    typeof value.payload === 'object'\n  );\n}\n\nfunction canSendMove(room) {\n  return room.state === MatchState.PLAYING && room.turn === room.selfSide && !room.lastError;\n}\n\nfunction applyMatchEvent(room, envelope) {\n  if (!isProtocolEnvelope(envelope)) {\n    return {\n      ...room,\n      state: MatchState.ERROR,\n      lastError: { code: 'INVALID_ENVELOPE', message: 'not a valid protocol envelope' },\n      lastEventAt: Date.now(),\n    };\n  }\n\n  const next = {\n    ...room,\n    lastEventAt: envelope.ts || Date.now(),\n  };\n\n  switch (envelope.type) {\n    case MatchEventType.REQUEST:\n      next.state = MatchState.MATCHING;\n      next.roomId = envelope.roomId || room.roomId;\n      next.seed = envelope.payload.seed ?? room.seed;\n      break;\n    case MatchEventType.ACCEPT:\n      next.state = MatchState.PLAYING;\n      next.roomId = envelope.roomId || room.roomId;\n      next.opponentId = envelope.payload.opponentId || room.opponentId;\n      next.selfSide = envelope.payload.selfSide || room.selfSide;\n      next.opponentSide = oppositeSide(next.selfSide);\n      next.turn = envelope.payload.selfSide || room.turn;\n      next.seed = envelope.payload.seed ?? room.seed;\n      next.result = null;\n      break;\n    case MatchEventType.REJECT:\n      next.state = MatchState.IDLE;\n      next.lastError = { code: 'MATCH_REJECTED', message: envelope.payload.reason || 'rejected' };\n      break;\n    case MatchEventType.SYNC:\n      next.state = MatchState.SYNCHRONIZING;\n      next.snapshot = envelope.payload.board || null;\n      next.turn = envelope.payload.turn || next.turn;\n      next.sequence = envelope.payload.moveSeq ?? next.sequence;\n      break;\n    case MatchEventType.MOVE:\n      next.sequence = Math.max(next.sequence, envelope.seq || 0) + 1;\n      next.turn = oppositeSide(room.turn);\n      next.moveLog = [...room.moveLog, envelope.payload.move];\n      next.state = MatchState.PLAYING;\n      break;\n    case MatchEventType.ACK:\n      next.lastAckSeq = Math.max(room.lastAckSeq, envelope.payload.ackSeq || 0);\n      break;\n    case MatchEventType.HEARTBEAT:\n      next.lastHeartbeatAt = envelope.ts || Date.now();\n      break;\n    case MatchEventType.RESIGN:\n      next.state = MatchState.FINISHED;\n      next.result = {\n        winner: envelope.senderId && envelope.senderId === room.selfId ? room.opponentSide : room.selfSide,\n        reason: 'resign',\n      };\n      break;\n    case MatchEventType.DRAW_OFFER:\n      next.pendingDraw = true;\n      break;\n    case MatchEventType.DRAW_RESPONSE:\n      next.pendingDraw = false;\n      if (envelope.payload.accepted) {\n        next.state = MatchState.FINISHED;\n        next.result = { winner: null, reason: 'draw' };\n      }\n      break;\n    case MatchEventType.ERROR:\n      next.state = MatchState.ERROR;\n      next.lastError = {\n        code: envelope.payload.code || 'UNKNOWN',\n        message: envelope.payload.message || 'unknown error',\n      };\n      break;\n    default:\n      next.lastError = { code: 'UNSUPPORTED_EVENT', message: envelope.type };\n      next.state = MatchState.ERROR;\n      break;\n  }\n\n  return next;\n}\n\nfunction describeMatchRoom(room) {\n  return {\n    roomId: room.roomId,\n    state: room.state,\n    turn: room.turn,\n    selfSide: room.selfSide,\n    opponentSide: room.opponentSide,\n    sequence: room.sequence,\n    lastAckSeq: room.lastAckSeq,\n    pendingDraw: room.pendingDraw,\n    hasSnapshot: Boolean(room.snapshot),\n    result: room.result,\n    error: room.lastError,\n  };\n}\n\nmodule.exports = {\n  PROTOCOL_VERSION,\n  MatchMode,\n  MatchState,\n  MatchEventType,\n  createMatchRoom,\n  createEnvelope,\n  createMatchRequest,\n  createMatchAccept,\n  createMoveEvent,\n  createAckEvent,\n  createSyncEvent,\n  createHeartbeatEvent,\n  createResignEvent,\n  createDrawOfferEvent,\n  createDrawResponseEvent,\n  createErrorEvent,\n  isProtocolEnvelope,\n  canSendMove,\n  applyMatchEvent,\n  describeMatchRoom,\n};\n","file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/utils/match-protocol.js","path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/utils/match-protocol.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"code889","model":"gpt-5.4-mini","usage":{"input":3592,"output":7117,"cacheRead":57856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68565,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774091009782}}
