{"type":"message","id":"e63d3c1f","parentId":"570c1a2c","timestamp":"2026-03-21T19:01:10.173Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering method aliases and UI**\n\nI'm thinking about using grep to find \"simulateIncoming\" in relation to WXML names. It seems I'll need to rename methods or add aliases in game.js to satisfy WXML and connect the controls. Adding alias methods like `simulateOnlineRequest()` to call `simulateIncomingRequest()` feels essential. I also want to add input for signal URLs and maybe create connect/disconnect buttons to enhance the UI. I'll patch WXML to include these UI elements.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0z4M467Rkj48dgoZm6ffWtcJ","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/game/game.js","limit":120,"offset":1,"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/game/game.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"code889","model":"gpt-5.4-mini","usage":{"input":3253,"output":1110,"cacheRead":60928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65291,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774119662872}}
{"type":"message","id":"ea99ad75","parentId":"e63d3c1f","timestamp":"2026-03-21T19:01:10.183Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0z4M467Rkj48dgoZm6ffWtcJ","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"const { createGameState } = require('../../utils/game-state');\nconst {\n  Side,\n  createInitialBoard,\n  cloneBoard,\n  getPieceAt,\n  getLegalMoves,\n  advanceGame,\n  searchBestMove,\n  pieceLabel,\n} = require('../../utils/chess-engine');\nconst {\n  MatchMode,\n  MatchState,\n  createMatchRoom,\n} = require('../../utils/match-protocol');\nconst {\n  TransportStatus,\n  createMatchSignalClient,\n} = require('../../utils/match-signal');\nconst { saveLastMatch, saveMatchRoom, loadMatchRoom } = require('../../utils/match-store');\n\nfunction coordKey(x, y) {\n  return `${x}:${y}`;\n}\n\nfunction formatCoord({ x, y }) {\n  return `(${x},${y})`;\n}\n\nfunction buildBoardView(board, selectedPieceId, legalMoves, hintMove, syncMarkers) {\n  const legalMap = new Set((legalMoves || []).map((move) => coordKey(move.to.x, move.to.y)));\n  const hintMap = hintMove\n    ? new Set([coordKey(hintMove.from.x, hintMove.from.y), coordKey(hintMove.to.x, hintMove.to.y)])\n    : new Set();\n  const syncMap = new Set((syncMarkers || []).map((move) => coordKey(move.x, move.y)));\n  const lastMoveMap = board.lastMove\n    ? new Set([coordKey(board.lastMove.from.x, board.lastMove.from.y), coordKey(board.lastMove.to.x, board.lastMove.to.y)])\n    : new Set();\n\n  const rows = [];\n  for (let y = 0; y < 10; y += 1) {\n    const cells = [];\n    for (let x = 0; x < 9; x += 1) {\n      const piece = getPieceAt(board, x, y);\n      const selected = piece && piece.id === selectedPieceId;\n      const legalTarget = legalMap.has(coordKey(x, y));\n      const hintTarget = hintMap.has(coordKey(x, y));\n      const syncTarget = syncMap.has(coordKey(x, y));\n      const lastMove = lastMoveMap.has(coordKey(x, y));\n      cells.push({\n        x,\n        y,\n        key: coordKey(x, y),\n        piece,\n        text: piece ? pieceLabel(piece) : '',\n        selected,\n        legalTarget,\n        hintTarget,\n        syncTarget,\n        lastMove,\n      });\n    }\n    rows.push({ y, cells });\n  }\n  return rows;\n}\n\nPage({\n  data: {\n    state: createGameState(),\n    board: createInitialBoard(),\n    boardRows: [],\n    selectedPieceId: null,\n    legalMoves: [],\n    hintMove: null,\n    hintText: '点击“提示”获取推荐走法',\n    matchRoom: createMatchRoom(),\n    connectionStatus: '未连接在线房间',\n    transportStatus: TransportStatus.IDLE,\n    signalUrl: '',\n    syncMarkers: [],\n    logLines: [],\n    tips: [\n      '点棋子选中，再点可落位置',\n      '红方先手，目前默认人机对战',\n      '提示会推荐当前回合的一步走法',\n      '在线匹配协议层已接入本地模拟房间'\n    ],\n  },\n\n  onLoad() {\n    this.boardHistory = [];\n    this.aiTimer = null;\n    const storedRoom = loadMatchRoom();\n    this.matchRoom = storedRoom || createMatchRoom({ mode: MatchMode.ONLINE, state: MatchState.IDLE });\n    this.signalClient = createMatchSignalClient({\n      room: this.matchRoom,\n      url: '',\n      onRoomChange: (room) => this.onRoomChange(room),\n      onTransportChange: (transport) => this.onTransportChange(transport),\n      onEnvelope: (envelope) => this.appendLog(`收到 ${envelope.type}`),\n      onError: (error) => this.appendLog(`错误：${error.code}`),\n    });\n    this.setData({ matchRoom: this.matchRoom, connectionStatus: this.describeConnection(this.matchRoom) });\n    this.refreshBoard('游戏页已就绪');\n  },\n\n  onUnload() {\n    if (this.aiTimer) clearTimeout(this.aiTimer);\n    if (this.signalClient) this.signalClient.dispose();\n  },\n\n  appendLog(line) {\n    const next = [line, ...this.data.logLines].slice(0, 8);\n    this.setData({ logLines: next });\n  },\n\n  onRoomChange(room) {\n    this.matchRoom = room;\n\n[391 more lines in file. Use offset=121 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774119670176}}
{"type":"message","id":"b60a52c6","parentId":"ea99ad75","timestamp":"2026-03-21T19:01:22.302Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Implementing connection features**\n\nI need to integrate some code changes and run tests to fix a naming mismatch between game.js and WXML. WXML is using simulateOnline*, while JS has simulateIncoming*. It looks like the signalUrl input is absent, so I'll implement a UI that includes connection controls. Since there's no backend endpoint, I might need to set up a WebSocket connection path with buttons to connect and disconnect. Also, updating the protocol layer with match request helpers is on my list, plus adding a mock transport adapter for offline use.\n\n**Implementing socket communication**\n\nI need to implement sending moves in game.js to signal if connected. I'll integrate commitMove to send moves using wx.connectSocket. In a mini-program, sendSocketMessage is global, and it should work if the socket is opened. My adapter uses task.send, but connectSocketTask has methods like onOpen and onMessage, not send. I should probably use wx.sendSocketMessage instead. I can't use task.send, but leaving that branch harmless could be okay. Lastly, I might want to check for code lint issues and inspect app.json for input components.\n\n**Refactoring for input fields**\n\nI need to implement bound fields in WXML, particularly using an input for signalUrl. It seems like there might not be page data binding, so I should add this input. This is part of a refactor, so I’ll carefully modify game.js and WXML, and maybe wxss as well. Additionally, I’ll connect the match-signal methods for sendMatchRequest and Accept. If there’s no URL, perhaps a local demo is needed. I might also create an auto-matching simulation based on protocol state, and I should consider running tests, although there may not be tests for the mini-program.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_vFfBAaLPkThMTovyLJo8VsUy","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/game/game.js","limit":200,"offset":121,"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/game/game.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"code889","model":"gpt-5.4-mini","usage":{"input":1242,"output":1110,"cacheRead":64000,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66352,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774119670182}}
{"type":"message","id":"1ea9c13a","parentId":"b60a52c6","timestamp":"2026-03-21T19:01:22.314Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_vFfBAaLPkThMTovyLJo8VsUy","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    this.setData({ matchRoom: room });\n    saveMatchRoom(room);\n    this.refreshBoard(`在线房间：${room.state}`);\n  },\n\n  onTransportChange(transport) {\n    this.setData({ transportStatus: transport.status, connectionStatus: this.describeTransport(transport) });\n  },\n\n  describeTransport(transport) {\n    if (!transport) return '未连接在线房间';\n    return `${transport.status}${transport.url ? ` · ${transport.url}` : ''}`;\n  },\n\n  describeConnection(room) {\n    if (!room) return '未连接在线房间';\n    if (room.state === MatchState.PLAYING) return `在线房间 ${room.roomId || '待分配'} · 可走子`;\n    if (room.state === MatchState.MATCHING) return `在线房间 ${room.roomId || '待分配'} · 匹配中`;\n    if (room.state === MatchState.SYNCHRONIZING) return `在线房间 ${room.roomId || '待分配'} · 同步中`;\n    if (room.state === MatchState.FINISHED) return `在线房间 ${room.roomId || '待分配'} · 已结束`;\n    if (room.state === MatchState.ERROR) return `在线房间 ${room.roomId || '待分配'} · 异常`;\n    return `在线房间 ${room.roomId || '待分配'} · 待开始`;\n  },\n\n  refreshBoard(message, overrideLegalMoves, overrideHintMove, overrideSyncMarkers) {\n    const legalMoves = getLegalMoves(this.data.board, this.data.board.currentSide);\n    const boardRows = buildBoardView(\n      this.data.board,\n      this.data.selectedPieceId,\n      overrideLegalMoves || this.data.legalMoves,\n      overrideHintMove === undefined ? this.data.hintMove : overrideHintMove,\n      overrideSyncMarkers === undefined ? this.data.syncMarkers : overrideSyncMarkers,\n    );\n    const summary = this.getStatusText(this.data.board, message);\n    this.setData({\n      state: {\n        ...this.data.state,\n        status: this.data.board.status,\n        winner: this.data.board.winner,\n        side: this.data.board.currentSide,\n        moveCount: this.data.board.moveHistory.length,\n        message: summary,\n      },\n      boardRows,\n      legalMoves,\n      boardLabel: summary,\n    });\n  },\n\n  getStatusText(board, fallback) {\n    if (board.status === 'checkmate') {\n      return board.winner === Side.RED ? '红方胜，已将死' : '黑方胜，已将死';\n    }\n    if (board.status === 'draw') return '平局';\n    if (board.status === 'check') return `${board.currentSide === Side.RED ? '红方' : '黑方'}被将军`;\n    return fallback || `${board.currentSide === Side.RED ? '红方' : '黑方'}走子`;\n  },\n\n  saveMatchResult(finalBoard) {\n    const winnerText = finalBoard.status === 'draw'\n      ? '平局'\n      : finalBoard.winner === Side.RED\n        ? '红方胜'\n        : '黑方胜';\n    const replayMoves = finalBoard.moveHistory.map((move) => ({\n      pieceId: move.pieceId,\n      from: move.from,\n      to: move.to,\n      capturedPieceId: move.capturedPieceId,\n    }));\n\n    saveLastMatch({\n      finishedAt: Date.now(),\n      status: finalBoard.status,\n      winner: finalBoard.winner,\n      winnerText,\n      moveCount: finalBoard.moveHistory.length,\n      summary: this.getStatusText(finalBoard),\n      moves: replayMoves,\n      finalBoard: cloneBoard(finalBoard),\n    });\n  },\n\n  persistMatchRoom(room) {\n    this.matchRoom = room;\n    this.setData({ matchRoom: room, connectionStatus: this.describeConnection(room) });\n    saveMatchRoom(room);\n  },\n\n  connectSignal() {\n    const url = this.data.signalUrl.trim();\n    if (!url) {\n      this.appendLog('请先填写信令地址');\n      return;\n    }\n    const ok = this.signalClient.connect(url);\n    if (ok) this.appendLog(`连接中：${url}`);\n  },\n\n  disconnectSignal() {\n    this.signalClient.disconnect();\n    this.appendLog('已断开信令连接');\n  },\n\n  sendRawEnvelope(envelope) {\n    const sent = this.signalClient.sendEnvelope(envelope);\n    this.appendLog(sent ? `发送 ${envelope.type}` : `发送失败 ${envelope.type}`);\n  },\n\n  sendQuickHeartbeat() {\n    this.sendRawEnvelope(this.signalClient.sendHeartbeat());\n  },\n\n  sendQuickSync() {\n    this.sendRawEnvelope(this.signalClient.sendSync(cloneBoard(this.data.board), this.data.board.currentSide, this.data.board.moveHistory.length));\n  },\n\n  sendQuickAck() {\n    this.sendRawEnvelope(this.signalClient.sendAck(this.matchRoom.sequence));\n  },\n\n  sendQuickDrawOffer() {\n    this.sendRawEnvelope(this.signalClient.sendDrawOffer());\n  },\n\n  sendQuickDrawResponse() {\n    this.sendRawEnvelope(this.signalClient.sendDrawResponse(true));\n  },\n\n  sendQuickResign() {\n    this.sendRawEnvelope(this.signalClient.sendResign());\n  },\n\n  sendQuickError() {\n    this.sendRawEnvelope(this.signalClient.sendError('NETWORK_ERROR', 'demo error'));\n  },\n\n  simulateIncomingRequest() {\n    const envelope = {\n      v: '1.0',\n      type: 'match.request',\n      roomId: this.matchRoom.roomId || 'room-demo-001',\n      senderId: 'remote-black',\n      seq: 1,\n      ts: Date.now(),\n      payload: { desiredSide: Side.BLACK, seed: 7 },\n    };\n    this.signalClient.applyIncomingEnvelope(envelope);\n    this.appendLog('模拟收到 request');\n  },\n\n  simulateIncomingAccept() {\n    const envelope = {\n      v: '1.0',\n      type: 'match.accept',\n      roomId: this.matchRoom.roomId || 'room-demo-001',\n      senderId: 'remote-black',\n      seq: 2,\n      ts: Date.now(),\n      payload: { opponentId: 'remote-black', selfSide: Side.RED, seed: 7 },\n    };\n    this.signalClient.applyIncomingEnvelope(envelope);\n    this.appendLog('模拟收到 accept');\n  },\n\n  simulateIncomingMove() {\n    const envelope = {\n      v: '1.0',\n      type: 'match.move',\n      roomId: this.matchRoom.roomId || 'room-demo-001',\n      senderId: 'remote-black',\n      seq: 3,\n      ts: Date.now(),\n      payload: { move: { pieceId: 'r-r1', from: { x: 0, y: 9 }, to: { x: 0, y: 8 } } },\n    };\n    this.signalClient.applyIncomingEnvelope(envelope);\n    this.appendLog('模拟收到 move');\n  },\n\n  simulateIncomingSync() {\n    const envelope = {\n      v: '1.0',\n      type: 'match.sync',\n      roomId: this.matchRoom.roomId || 'room-demo-001',\n      senderId: 'remote-black',\n      seq: 4,\n      ts: Date.now(),\n      payload: { board: cloneBoard(this.data.board), turn: this.data.board.currentSide, moveSeq: this.data.board.moveHistory.length },\n    };\n    this.signalClient.applyIncomingEnvelope(envelope);\n    this.setData({ syncMarkers: this.data.board.lastMove ? [this.data.board.lastMove.from, this.data.board.lastMove.to] : [] });\n    this.appendLog('模拟收到 sync');\n  },\n\n  simulateIncomingHeartbeat() {\n    this.signalClient.applyIncomingEnvelope({\n      v: '1.0',\n      type: 'match.heartbeat',\n      roomId: this.matchRoom.roomId || 'room-demo-001',\n      senderId: 'remote-black',\n\n[191 more lines in file. Use offset=321 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774119682305}}
{"type":"message","id":"98f9d396","parentId":"1ea9c13a","timestamp":"2026-03-21T19:01:28.249Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_sC57lV86oss2PJBLQFQLQUrZ","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/game/game.js","limit":220,"offset":321,"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/pages/game/game.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"code889","model":"gpt-5.4-mini","usage":{"input":1987,"output":418,"cacheRead":65024,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67429,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774119682312}}
{"type":"message","id":"59a7a494","parentId":"98f9d396","timestamp":"2026-03-21T19:01:28.260Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_sC57lV86oss2PJBLQFQLQUrZ","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"      seq: 5,\n      ts: Date.now(),\n      payload: { ping: Date.now() },\n    });\n    this.appendLog('模拟收到 heartbeat');\n  },\n\n  simulateIncomingDrawOffer() {\n    this.signalClient.applyIncomingEnvelope({\n      v: '1.0',\n      type: 'match.draw.offer',\n      roomId: this.matchRoom.roomId || 'room-demo-001',\n      senderId: 'remote-black',\n      seq: 6,\n      ts: Date.now(),\n      payload: {},\n    });\n    this.appendLog('模拟收到 draw.offer');\n  },\n\n  simulateIncomingError() {\n    this.signalClient.applyIncomingEnvelope({\n      v: '1.0',\n      type: 'match.error',\n      roomId: this.matchRoom.roomId || 'room-demo-001',\n      senderId: 'remote-black',\n      seq: 7,\n      ts: Date.now(),\n      payload: { code: 'NETWORK_ERROR', message: 'mock offline' },\n    });\n    this.appendLog('模拟收到 error');\n  },\n\n  resetMatchRoom() {\n    const room = createMatchRoom({ roomId: 'room-demo-001', selfId: 'local-red', selfSide: Side.RED, mode: MatchMode.ONLINE, state: MatchState.IDLE });\n    this.persistMatchRoom(room);\n    this.setData({ syncMarkers: [] });\n    this.appendLog('在线房间已重置');\n    this.refreshBoard('在线房间已重置');\n  },\n\n  resetGame() {\n    if (this.aiTimer) clearTimeout(this.aiTimer);\n    this.boardHistory = [];\n    this.setData({\n      board: createInitialBoard(),\n      selectedPieceId: null,\n      legalMoves: [],\n      hintMove: null,\n      hintText: '点击“提示”获取推荐走法',\n      syncMarkers: [],\n    });\n    this.refreshBoard('对局已重开');\n  },\n\n  undoMove() {\n    if (!this.boardHistory || !this.boardHistory.length) return;\n    if (this.aiTimer) clearTimeout(this.aiTimer);\n\n    const stepsToUndo = this.data.state.mode === 'ai' && this.data.board.currentSide === Side.RED ? 2 : 1;\n    let previous = null;\n    for (let i = 0; i < stepsToUndo; i += 1) {\n      if (!this.boardHistory.length) break;\n      previous = this.boardHistory.pop();\n    }\n    if (!previous) return;\n\n    this.setData({\n      board: cloneBoard(previous),\n      selectedPieceId: null,\n      legalMoves: [],\n      hintMove: null,\n      hintText: stepsToUndo === 2 ? '已悔棋两步，轮到你重新落子' : '已悔棋一步',\n    });\n    this.refreshBoard(stepsToUndo === 2 ? '已悔棋两步' : '已悔棋一步');\n  },\n\n  showHint() {\n    if (this.data.board.status === 'checkmate' || this.data.board.status === 'draw') {\n      this.setData({ hintMove: null, hintText: '对局已结束，无法提示' });\n      this.refreshBoard('对局已结束');\n      return;\n    }\n    if (this.data.board.currentSide !== Side.RED) {\n      this.setData({ hintMove: null, hintText: '当前轮到黑方，先等 AI 走完' });\n      this.refreshBoard('当前轮到黑方');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    const hintMove = searchBestMove(this.data.board, { side: Side.RED, depth: 2, timeLimitMs: 60 });\n    if (!hintMove) {\n      this.setData({ hintMove: null, hintText: '当前没有可用提示' });\n      this.refreshBoard('当前没有可用提示');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    const piece = getPieceAt(this.data.board, hintMove.from.x, hintMove.from.y);\n    const hintText = `${piece ? pieceLabel(piece) : '棋子'} 建议走 ${formatCoord(hintMove.from)} → ${formatCoord(hintMove.to)}`;\n    this.setData({\n      hintMove,\n      hintText,\n      selectedPieceId: piece ? piece.id : null,\n      legalMoves: getLegalMoves(this.data.board, Side.RED).filter((move) => move.pieceId === hintMove.pieceId),\n    });\n    this.refreshBoard('已给出提示', this.data.legalMoves, hintMove);\n  },\n\n  onCellTap(e) {\n    if (this.data.board.status === 'checkmate' || this.data.board.status === 'draw') return;\n    if (this.data.board.currentSide === Side.BLACK) return;\n\n    const x = Number(e.currentTarget.dataset.x);\n    const y = Number(e.currentTarget.dataset.y);\n    const piece = getPieceAt(this.data.board, x, y);\n    const selectedPieceId = this.data.selectedPieceId;\n    const selectedMoves = this.data.legalMoves;\n    const legalMove = selectedMoves.find((move) => move.to.x === x && move.to.y === y);\n\n    if (legalMove) {\n      this.commitMove(legalMove, '你走了一步');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    if (piece && piece.side === Side.RED && this.data.board.currentSide === Side.RED) {\n      const moves = getLegalMoves(this.data.board, Side.RED).filter((move) => move.pieceId === piece.id);\n      this.setData({\n        selectedPieceId: piece.id,\n        legalMoves: moves,\n        hintMove: null,\n        hintText: `已选中 ${pieceLabel(piece)}，可落点已高亮`,\n      });\n      this.refreshBoard(`${pieceLabel(piece)}已选中`, moves, null);\n      return;\n    }\n\n    if (selectedPieceId) {\n      this.setData({ selectedPieceId: null, legalMoves: [], hintMove: null, hintText: '已取消选中' });\n      this.refreshBoard('取消选中', [], null);\n    }\n  },\n\n  finishIfNeeded(nextBoard) {\n    if (nextBoard.status === 'playing') return false;\n    this.saveMatchResult(nextBoard);\n    const resultUrl = `/pages/result/result?status=${nextBoard.status}&winner=${nextBoard.winner || ''}`;\n    wx.reLaunch({ url: resultUrl });\n    return true;\n  },\n\n  commitMove(move, message) {\n    this.boardHistory.push(cloneBoard(this.data.board));\n    const nextBoard = advanceGame(this.data.board, move);\n    this.setData({\n      board: nextBoard,\n      selectedPieceId: null,\n      legalMoves: [],\n      hintMove: null,\n      hintText: message,\n    });\n    this.refreshBoard(message, [], null);\n\n    if (this.finishIfNeeded(nextBoard)) return;\n\n    if (nextBoard.status === 'playing' && nextBoard.currentSide === Side.BLACK) {\n      this.scheduleAiMove();\n    }\n  },\n\n  scheduleAiMove() {\n    if (this.aiTimer) clearTimeout(this.aiTimer);\n    this.aiTimer = setTimeout(() => {\n      this.aiTimer = null;\n      const move = searchBestMove(this.data.board, { side: Side.BLACK, depth: 1, timeLimitMs: 80 });\n      if (!move) {\n        this.setData({ hintMove: null, hintText: 'AI 无合法走法' });\n        this.refreshBoard('AI 无合法走法');\n        return;\n      }\n      this.commitMove(move, 'AI 已落子');\n    }, 180);\n  },\n\n  startGame() {\n    this.resetGame();\n  },\n\n  goResult() {\n    wx.navigateTo({ url: '/pages/result/result' });\n  },\n});\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774119688252}}
{"type":"message","id":"6f9a896e","parentId":"59a7a494","timestamp":"2026-03-21T19:01:41.366Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating project updates**\n\nI need to make some changes because the current method names don't match WXML. It’s essential to wire the actual transport layer better and check for any missing input buttons in WXML. Adding a real connection UI path is important, possibly with local fallbacks. I’m thinking of integrating `sendMove` for local moves and managing incoming moves for board updates. The user likely wants the next step, so let’s add input fields for `signalUrl` and connect/disconnect buttons to enhance the transport. I should also consider adapting `game.js` for requests and accept actions.\n\n**Fixing connection issues**\n\nI recalled steps earlier, but now I can proceed with fixing issues. The WXML buttons are bound to `simulateOnlineRequest`, whereas they should link to `simulateIncomingRequest`. I could rename them or add aliases that wouldn't require changing WXML. Also, I’ll need to implement connection UI fields, specifically for `signalUrl` with connect/disconnect buttons. We might need a local fallback adapter in `match-signal` if `wx` is unavailable. For the mini program, `wx.connectSocket` will be useful, supporting both sending and closing methods, and I'll work on a helper for generating local room actions.\n\n**Improving heartbeat configuration**\n\nI noticed that when sending a heartbeat from the UI, there's no input for the actual URL. So, I should expose a config input in WXML. I might need to add an `onInputSignalUrl` function and utilize `wx.setData`. Additionally, I should integrate handling for remote moves to apply incoming move envelopes directly to the board, not just the room. The user seems to want a connection between the match abstraction and the websocket layer. Currently, `game.js` only logs incoming envelopes, but it should react to updates and apply changes to the board as needed.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_BrLwIT6FBCvAYBEPmf2tcXNH","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -RIn \"function advanceGame\\|module.exports = {\" /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/chinese-chess-minigame/miniprogram/utils/chess-engine.js | sed -n '1,120p'","workdir":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"code889","model":"gpt-5.4-mini","usage":{"input":2156,"output":1364,"cacheRead":66560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70080,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774119688259}}
